49 template<unsigned int spacedim>
50 class OmegaFluxDissipation00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
51 {
52 
53 private:
54 
58  const double D;
59 
60 public:
61 
79  OmegaFluxDissipation00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
80  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
81  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
82  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
83  const double D,
84  const unsigned int method,
85  const double alpha = 0.0)
86  :
87  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 3, 0, 0, 1, method, alpha, "OmegaFluxDissipation00"),
88  D(D)
89  {
90  }
91 
95  bool
96  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
97  const double /*t*/,
98  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
99  double& omega,
100  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
101  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
102  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
103  const bool compute_dq)
104  const
105  {
106  dealii::Tensor<1, 3> i;
107  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
108  i[m] = values[m];
109  const double q = values[3] > 1e-16 ? values[3] : 1e-16;
110 
111  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
112  {
113  omega = 1.0 / ( 2.0 * D * q) * i * i;
114  }
115 
116  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
117  {
118  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
119  d_omega[m] = 1.0 / ( D * q ) * i[m];
120  }
121 
122  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
123  {
124  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
125  d2_omega(m, m) = 1.0 / ( D * q );
126 
127  if(compute_dq && (q > 1e-16))
128  {
129  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
130  d2_omega(m, 3) = - 1.0 / ( D * q * q ) * i[m];
131  }
132  }
133 
134  return false;
135  }
136 
137 };

156 template<unsigned int spacedim>
157 class OmegaDualFluxDissipation00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
158 {
159 
160 private:
161 
165  const double D;
166 
167 public:
168 
186  OmegaDualFluxDissipation00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
187  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
188  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
189  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
190  const double D,
191  const unsigned int method,
192  const double alpha = 0.0)
193  :
194  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 0, 0, 3, 1, method, alpha, "OmegaDualFluxDissipation00"),
195  D(D)
196  {
197  }
198 
202  bool
203  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
204  const double /*t*/,
205  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
206  double& omega,
207  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
208  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
209  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
210  const bool compute_dq)
211  const
212  {
213  dealii::Tensor<1, 3> E;
214  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
215  E[m] = values[m];
216  const double q = values[3];
217 
218  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
219  {
220  omega = -D * q / 2.0 * E * E;
221  }
222 
223  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
224  {
225  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
226  d_omega[m] = -D * q * E[m];
227  }
228 
229  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
230  {
231  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
232  d2_omega(m, m) = -D * q;
233 
234  if(compute_dq)
235  {
236  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
237  d2_omega(m, 3) = -D * E[m];
238  }
239  }
240 
241 
242  return false;
243  }
244

257 template<unsigned int spacedim>
258 class OmegaMixedTerm00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
259 {
260 
261 public:
262 
278  OmegaMixedTerm00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
279  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
280  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
281  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
282  const unsigned int method,
283  const double alpha = 0.0)
284  :
285  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 0, 1, 1, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaMixedTerm00")
286  {
287  }
288 
292  bool
293  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
294  const double /*t*/,
295  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
296  double& omega,
297  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
298  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
299  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
300  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
301  const
302  {
303  const double c_dot = values[0];
304  const double eta = values[1];
305 
306  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
307  {
308  omega = -c_dot * eta;
309  }
310 
311  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
312  {
313  d_omega[0] = -eta;
314  d_omega[1] = -c_dot;
315  }
316 
317  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
318  {
319  d2_omega(0, 0) = d2_omega(1, 1) = 0.0;
320  d2_omega(0, 1) = d2_omega(1, 0) = -1.0;
321  }
322 
323  return false;
324  }

342 template<unsigned int spacedim>
343 class OmegaMixedTerm01 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
344 {
345 
346 public:
347 
363  OmegaMixedTerm01( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
364  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
365  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
366  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
367  const unsigned int method,
368  const double alpha = 0.0)
369  :
370  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 0, 3, 3, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaMixedTerm01")
371  {
372  }
373 
377  bool
378  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
379  const double /*t*/,
380  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
381  double& omega,
382  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
383  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
384  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
385  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
386  const
387  {
388  const double D_x = values[0];
389  const double D_y = values[1];
390  const double D_z = values[2];
391  const double E_x = values[3];
392  const double E_y = values[4];
393  const double E_z = values[5];
394 
395  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
396  {
397  omega = - D_x * E_x - D_y * E_y - D_z * E_z;
398  }
399 
400  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
401  {
402  d_omega[0] = -E_x;
403  d_omega[1] = -E_y;
404  d_omega[2] = -E_z;
405  d_omega[3] = -D_x;
406  d_omega[4] = -D_y;
407  d_omega[5] = -D_z;
408  }
409 
410  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
411  {
412  d2_omega(0, 3) = d2_omega(3, 0) = -1.0;
413  d2_omega(1, 4) = d2_omega(4, 1) = -1.0;
414  d2_omega(2, 5) = d2_omega(5, 2) = -1.0;
415  }
416 
417  return false;
418  }

517 template<unsigned int spacedim>
518 class OmegaDivergenceConstraint00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
519 {
520 
521 public:
522 
538  OmegaDivergenceConstraint00(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
539  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
540  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
541  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
542  const unsigned int method,
543  const double alpha = 0.0)
544  :
545  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 1, 1, 1, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaDivergenceConstraint00")
546  {
547  }
548 
552  bool
553  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
554  const double /*t*/,
555  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
556  double& omega,
557  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
558  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
559  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
560  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
561  const
562  {
563  const double div_I_dot = values[0];
564  const double c_dot = values[1];
565  const double mu = values[2];
566 
567 
568  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
569  {
570  omega = -mu * (div_I_dot + c_dot);
571  }
572 
573  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
574  {
575  d_omega[0] = -mu;
576  d_omega[1] = -mu;
577  d_omega[2] = -(div_I_dot + c_dot);
578  }
579 
580  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
581  {
582  d2_omega(0, 2) = d2_omega(2, 0) = -1.0;
583  d2_omega(1, 2) = d2_omega(2, 1) = -1.0;
584  }
585 
586  return false;
587  }
588

605 template<unsigned int spacedim>
606 class OmegaZeroNormalFlux00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
607 {
608 
609 public:
610 
626  OmegaZeroNormalFlux00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_sigma,
627  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
628  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
629  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
630  const unsigned int method,
631  const double alpha = 0.0)
632  :
633  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_sigma, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 3, 0, 1, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaZeroNormalFlux00")
634  {
635  }
636 
640  bool
641  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
642  const double /*t*/,
643  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
644  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& n,
645  double& sigma,
646  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
647  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
648  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
649  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
650  const
651  {
652  const double I_x_dot = values[0];
653  const double I_y_dot = values[1];
654  const double I_z_dot = values[2];
655  const double mu = values[3];
656  const double n_x = n[0];
657  const double n_y = n[1];
658  const double n_z = spacedim==3 ? n[2] : 0.0;
659 
660  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
661  {
662  sigma = -mu * (I_x_dot * n_x + I_y_dot * n_y + I_z_dot * n_z);
663  }
664 
665  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
666  {
667  d_sigma[0] = -mu * n_x;
668  d_sigma[1] = -mu * n_y;
669  d_sigma[2] = -mu * n_z;
670  d_sigma[3] = -(I_x_dot * n_x + I_y_dot * n_y + I_z_dot * n_z);
671  }
672 
673  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
674  {
675  d2_sigma(0, 3) = d2_sigma(3, 0) = -n_x;
676  d2_sigma(1, 3) = d2_sigma(3, 1) = -n_y;
677  d2_sigma(2, 3) = d2_sigma(3, 2) = -n_z;
678  }
679 
680  return false;
681  }
682 
683 };

697 template<unsigned int spacedim>
698 class OmegaFluxPower00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
699 {
700 private:
701 
705  dealii::Function<spacedim>&
706  function_mu;
707 
708 public:
709 
727  OmegaFluxPower00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_sigma,
728  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
729  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
730  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
731  dealii::Function<spacedim>& function_mu,
732  const unsigned int method,
733  const double alpha = 0.0)
734  :
735  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_sigma, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 3, 0, 0, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaFluxPower00"),
736  function_mu(function_mu)
737  {
738  }
739 
743  bool
744  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
745  const double t,
746  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& x,
747  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& n,
748  double& sigma,
749  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
750  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& /*d2_sigma*/,
751  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
752  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
753  const
754  {
755  const double time_old = function_mu.get_time();
756  function_mu.set_time(t);
757  const double mu_bar = function_mu.value(x);
758  function_mu.set_time(time_old);
759 
760  const double I_x_dot = values[0];
761  const double I_y_dot = values[1];
762  const double I_z_dot = values[2];
763  const double n_x = n[0];
764  const double n_y = n[1];
765  const double n_z = spacedim==3 ? n[2] : 0.0;
766 
767  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
768  {
769  sigma = mu_bar * (I_x_dot * n_x + I_y_dot * n_y + I_z_dot * n_z);
770  }
771 
772  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
773  {
774  d_sigma[0] = mu_bar * n_x;
775  d_sigma[1] = mu_bar * n_y;
776  d_sigma[2] = mu_bar * n_z;
777  }
778 
779  return false;
780  }
781 
782 };

794 template<unsigned int spacedim>

802  dealii::Function<spacedim>&
803  function_i;

811  is_active = true;

813 
831  OmegaDualFluxPower00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_sigma,
832  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
833  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
834  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
835  dealii::Function<spacedim>& function_i,
836  const unsigned int method,
837  const double alpha = 0.0)
838  :
839  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_sigma, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 0, 0, 1, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaDualFluxPower00"),
840  function_i(function_i)

842  }
843 
847  bool
848  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
849  const double t,
850  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& x,
851  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& /*n*/,
852  double& sigma,
853  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
854  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& /*d2_sigma*/,
855  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
856  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
857  const
858  {
859  if(is_active)
860  {
861  const double time_old = function_i.get_time();
862  function_i.set_time(t);
863  const double i_bar = function_i.value(x);
864  function_i.set_time(time_old);
865 
866  const double eta = values[0];
867 
868  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
869  sigma = -i_bar * eta;
870 
871  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
872  d_sigma[0] = - i_bar;
873  }
874 
875  return false;
876  }

893 template<unsigned int spacedim>
894 class OmegaTraction00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
895 {
896 private:
897 
901  dealii::Function<spacedim>&
902  function_f;
903 
904 public:
905 
923  OmegaTraction00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_sigma,
924  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
925  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
926  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
927  dealii::Function<spacedim>& function_f,
928  const unsigned int method,
929  const double alpha = 0.0)
930  :
931  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_sigma, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 0, 3, 0, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaTraction00"),
932  function_f(function_f)
933  {
934  }
935 
939  bool
940  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
941  const double t,
942  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& x,
943  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& /*n*/,
944  double& sigma,
945  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
946  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& /*d2_sigma*/,
947  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
948  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
949  const
950  {
951 
952  const double time_old = function_f.get_time();
953  function_f.set_time(t);
954  const double f_x = function_f.value(x, 0);
955  const double f_y = function_f.value(x, 1);
956  const double f_z = function_f.value(x, 2);
957  function_f.set_time(time_old);
958 
959  const double u_x_dot = values[0];
960  const double u_y_dot = values[1];
961  const double u_z_dot = values[2];
962 
963  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
964  {
965  sigma = - (f_x * u_x_dot + f_y * u_y_dot + f_z * u_z_dot);
966  }
967 
968  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
969  {
970  d_sigma[0] = -f_x;
971  d_sigma[1] = -f_y;
972  d_sigma[2] = -f_z;
973  }
974 
975  return false;
976  }
977

992 template<unsigned int spacedim>
993 class OmegaInterfaceFluxDissipation00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
994 {
995 private:
996 
1000  const double
1001  D;
1002 
1003 public:
1004 
1022  OmegaInterfaceFluxDissipation00(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_sigma,
1023  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
1024  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
1025  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
1026  const double D,

1028  const double alpha = 0.0)
1029  :
1030  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_sigma, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 3, 0, 0, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaInterfaceFluxDissipation00"),
1031  D(D)
1032  {
1033  }
1034 
1038  bool
1039  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
1040  const double /*t*/,
1041  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
1042  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& n,
1043  double& sigma,
1044  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
1045  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
1046  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
1047  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
1048  const
1049  {
1050 
1051  const double I_x_dot = values[0];
1052  const double I_y_dot = values[1];
1053  const double I_z_dot = values[2];
1054  const double n_x = n[0];
1055  const double n_y = n[1];
1056  const double n_z = spacedim==3 ? n[2] : 0.0;
1057 
1058  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
1059  {
1060  sigma = 1.0/(2.0*D) * (I_x_dot * n_x + I_y_dot * n_y + I_z_dot * n_z) * (I_x_dot * n_x + I_y_dot * n_y + I_z_dot * n_z);
1061  }
1062 
1063  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
1064  {
1065  d_sigma[0] = 1.0/D * (I_x_dot * n_x + I_y_dot * n_y + I_z_dot * n_z) * n_x;
1066  d_sigma[1] = 1.0/D * (I_x_dot * n_x + I_y_dot * n_y + I_z_dot * n_z) * n_y;
1067  d_sigma[2] = 1.0/D * (I_x_dot * n_x + I_y_dot * n_y + I_z_dot * n_z) * n_z;
1068  }
1069 
1070  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
1071  {
1072  d2_sigma(0,0) = 1.0/D * n_x * n_x;
1073  d2_sigma(0,1) = 1.0/D * n_y * n_x;
1074  d2_sigma(0,2) = 1.0/D * n_z * n_x;
1075  d2_sigma(1,0) = 1.0/D * n_x * n_y;
1076  d2_sigma(1,1) = 1.0/D * n_y * n_y;
1077  d2_sigma(1,2) = 1.0/D * n_z * n_y;
1078  d2_sigma(2,0) = 1.0/D * n_x * n_z;
1079  d2_sigma(2,1) = 1.0/D * n_y * n_z;
1080  d2_sigma(2,2) = 1.0/D * n_z * n_z;
1081  }
1082 
1083  return false;
1084  }
1085 
1086 };

1098 template<unsigned int spacedim>
1099 class OmegaDualButlerVolmer00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
1100 {
1101 private:
1102 
1106  const double
1107  I_0;
1108 
1112  const double
1113  beta;
1114 
1118  const double
1119  RT;
1120 
1125  const double
1126  threshold;
1127 
1128 public:
1129 
1153  OmegaDualButlerVolmer00(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_sigma,
1154  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
1155  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
1156  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
1157  const double I_0,
1158  const double beta,
1159  const double RT,
1160  const double threshold,
1161  const unsigned int method,
1162  const double alpha = 0.0)
1163  :
1164  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_sigma, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 0, 0, 1, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaDualButlerVolmer00"),
1165  I_0(I_0),
1166  beta(beta),
1167  RT(RT),
1168  threshold(threshold)
1169  {
1170  }
1171 
1175  bool
1176  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
1177  const double /*t*/,
1178  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
1179  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& /*n*/,
1180  double& sigma,
1181  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
1182  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
1183  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
1184  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
1185  const
1186  {
1187 
1188  const double eta = values[0];
1189 
1190  double t1, t2;
1191 
1192  if(eta / RT > threshold)
1193  {
1194  t1 = exp(beta * threshold);
1195  t2 = exp( (beta - 1.0) * threshold);
1196  }
1197  else if(eta / RT < -threshold)
1198  {
1199  t1 = exp(-beta * threshold);
1200  t2 = exp( -(beta - 1.0) * threshold);
1201  }
1202  else
1203  {
1204  t1 = exp(beta * eta / RT);
1205  t2 = exp( (beta - 1.0) * eta / RT);
1206  }
1207 
1208  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
1209  {
1210  if(eta / RT > threshold)
1211  sigma = t1 / beta + t2 / (1.0 - beta) + (t1 - t2) * (eta / RT - threshold) + 0.5 * (beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2) * (eta / RT - threshold) * (eta / RT - threshold);
1212  else if(eta / RT < -threshold)
1213  sigma = t1 / beta + t2 / (1.0 - beta) + (t1 - t2) * (eta / RT + threshold) + 0.5 * (beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2) * (eta / RT + threshold) * (eta / RT + threshold);
1214  else
1215  sigma = t1/beta + t2/(1.0 - beta);
1216  sigma *= -I_0;
1217  }
1218 
1219  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
1220  {
1221  if(eta / RT > threshold)
1222  {
1223  d_sigma[0] = (t1 - t2) + (beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2) * (eta / RT - threshold);
1224  }
1225  else if(eta / RT < -threshold)
1226  {
1227  d_sigma[0] = (t1 - t2) + (beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2) * (eta / RT + threshold);
1228  }
1229  else
1230  {
1231  d_sigma[0] = (t1 - t2);
1232  }
1233  d_sigma[0] *= -I_0 / RT;
1234  }
1235 
1236  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
1237  {
1238  if(eta / RT > threshold)
1239  {
1240  d2_sigma(0,0) = beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2;
1241  }
1242  else if(eta / RT < -threshold)
1243  {
1244  d2_sigma(0,0) = beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2;
1245  }
1246  else
1247  {
1248  d2_sigma(0,0) = beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2;
1249  }
1250  d2_sigma(0,0) *= -I_0 / RT / RT;
1251  }
1252 
1253  return false;
1254  }
1255 
1256 };
1257 
1258 
1276 template<unsigned int spacedim>
1277 class OmegaDisplacementCoupling00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
1278 {
1279 
1280 private:
1281 
1285  const bool
1286  u_1_as_parameter;
1287 
1288 public:
1289 
1307  OmegaDisplacementCoupling00(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_sigma,
1308  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
1309  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
1310  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,

1312  const unsigned int method,
1313  const double alpha = 0.0)
1314  :
1315  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_sigma, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 0, 6, 3, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaDisplacementCoupling00"),
1316  u_1_as_parameter(u_1_as_parameter)
1317  {
1318  }
1319 
1323  bool
1324  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
1325  const double /*t*/,
1326  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
1327  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& /*n*/,
1328  double& sigma,
1329  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
1330  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
1331  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
1332  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
1333  const
1334  {
1335 
1336  dealii::Tensor<1,3> u_0, u_1, t;
1337 
1338  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1339  {
1340  u_0[m] = values[m];
1341  u_1[m] = values[m+3];
1342  t[m] = values[m+6];
1343  }
1344 
1345  const dealii::Tensor<1,3> u_0_u_1 = u_0 - u_1;
1346 
1347 
1348  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
1349  {
1350  sigma = t * u_0_u_1;
1351  }
1352 
1353  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
1354  {
1355  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1356  {
1357  d_sigma[m] = t[m];
1358  if(u_1_as_parameter)
1359  d_sigma[m+3] = 0.0;
1360  else
1361  d_sigma[m+3] = -t[m];
1362  d_sigma[m+6] = u_0_u_1[m];
1363  }
1364  }
1365 
1366  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
1367  {
1368  d2_sigma.reinit(9,9);
1369  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1370  {
1371  d2_sigma(m, m+6) = d2_sigma(m+6, m) = 1.0;
1372  if(!u_1_as_parameter)
1373  d2_sigma(m+3, m+6) = -1.0;
1374  d2_sigma(m+6, m+3) = -1.0;
1375  }
1376  }
1377 
1378  return false;
1379  }
1380

1418 template<unsigned int spacedim>
1419 class OmegaDualIonDissipation00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
1420 {
1421 
1422 private:
1423 
1427  const double
1428  D;
1429 
1433  const double
1434  V_m_f;
1435 
1436 
1437 public:
1438 
1458  OmegaDualIonDissipation00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
1459  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
1460  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
1461  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
1462  const double D,
1463  const double V_m_f,
1464  const unsigned int method,
1465  const double alpha = 0.0)
1466  :
1467  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 1, 0, 4, 11, method, alpha, "OmegaDualIonDissipation00"),
1468  D(D),
1469  V_m_f(V_m_f)
1470  {
1471  }
1472 
1476  bool
1477  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
1478  const double /*t*/,
1479  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
1480  double& omega,
1481  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
1482  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
1483  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
1484  const bool compute_dq)
1485  const
1486  {
1487 
1488  const double c_dot = values[0];
1489  dealii::Tensor<1,3> grad_eta;
1490  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1491  grad_eta[m] = values[m+1];
1492  const double eta = values[4];
1493  const double c = values[5];
1494  const double c_f = values[6];
1495  dealii::Tensor<2, 3> F, C, C_inv;
1496  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1497  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
1498  F[m][n] = values[7 + m * 3 + n];
1499  C = transpose(F) * F;
1500  C_inv = invert(C);
1501  const double J = determinant(F);
1502  const double n_f = c_f / J * V_m_f;
1503  const dealii::Tensor<1, 3> A = C_inv * grad_eta;
1504  const double grad_eta_C_inv_grad_eta = A * grad_eta;
1505 
1506  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
1507  {
1508  omega = -0.5 * D * c / n_f * grad_eta_C_inv_grad_eta - eta * c_dot;
1509  }
1510 
1511  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
1512  {
1513  d_omega[0] = -eta;
1514  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1515  d_omega[m + 1] = -D * c / n_f * A[m];
1516  d_omega[4] = -c_dot;
1517  }
1518 
1519  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
1520  {
1521  d2_omega = 0.0;
1522  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1523  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
1524  d2_omega(m + 1, n + 1) = -D * c / n_f * C_inv[m][n];
1525  d2_omega(0, 4) = d2_omega(4, 0) = -1.0;
1526 
1527  if(compute_dq)
1528  {
1529  const dealii::Tensor<1,3> F_A = F * A;
1530  const dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_C_inv = F * C_inv;
1531  dealii::Vector<double> F_vect(9), dJ_dF(9);
1532  for(unsigned i = 0; i < 9; ++i)
1533  F_vect[i] = values[7 + i];
1534  get_dJ_dF(F_vect, dJ_dF);
1535 
1536  for(unsigned int L = 0; L < 3; ++L)
1537  {
1538  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1539  for(unsigned int M = 0; M < 3; ++M)
1540  d2_omega[1 + L][7 + m * 3 + M] = (- D / V_m_f * A[L] * dJ_dF[m * 3 + M] + D * J / V_m_f * (C_inv[L][M] * F_A[m] + A[M] * F_C_inv[m][L] ) ) * c / c_f;
1541  d2_omega[1 + L][5] = - D * J / V_m_f * 1.0 / c_f * A[L];
1542  d2_omega[1 + L][6] = D * J / V_m_f * c / c_f / c_f * A[L];
1543  }
1544  }
1545 
1546 
1547  }
1548 
1549  return false;
1550 
1551  }
1552 
1553 };
1554

1745 template<unsigned int spacedim>
1746 class OmegaDualFluidDissipation00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
1747 {
1748 
1749 private:
1750 
1754  const unsigned int
1755  I;
1756 
1760  const double
1761  D;
1762 
1766  const double
1767  V_m_f;
1768 
1769 
1770 public:
1771 
1793  OmegaDualFluidDissipation00(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
1794  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
1795  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
1796  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
1797  const unsigned int I,
1798  const double D,
1799  const double V_m_f,
1800  const unsigned int method,
1801  const double alpha = 0.0)
1802  :
1803  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 1, 0, 4+3*I, 10+I, method, alpha, "OmegaDualFluidDissipation00"),
1804  I(I),
1805  D(D),
1806  V_m_f(V_m_f)
1807  {
1808  }
1809 
1813  bool
1814  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
1815  const double /*t*/,
1816  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
1817  double& omega,
1818  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
1819  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
1820  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
1821  const bool compute_dq)
1822  const
1823  {
1824  // start indices for respective quantities
1825  const unsigned int i_c_f_dot = 0;
1826  const unsigned int i_grad_eta_f = 1;
1827  vector<unsigned int> i_grad_eta_i(I);
1828  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
1829  i_grad_eta_i[i] = 4 + 3*i;
1830  const unsigned int i_eta_f = 4 + 3*I;
1831  const unsigned int i_c_f = 5 + 3*I;
1832  vector<unsigned int> i_c_i(I);
1833  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
1834  i_c_i[i] = 6 + 3*I + i;
1835  const unsigned int i_F = 6 + 4*I;
1836 
1837 
1838  const double c_f_dot = values[i_c_f_dot];
1839  const double c_f = values[i_c_f];
1840  dealii::Vector<double> c_i(I);
1841  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
1842  c_i[i] = values[i_c_i[i]];
1843 
1844  dealii::Tensor<1,3> grad_eta, grad_eta_f;
1845  std::vector<dealii::Tensor<1,3>> grad_eta_i(I);
1846  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1847  {
1848  grad_eta[m] = values[i_grad_eta_f + m];
1849  grad_eta_f[m] = values[i_grad_eta_f + m];
1850  }
1851  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
1852  {
1853  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1854  {
1855  grad_eta[m] += c_i[i]/c_f * values[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m];
1856  grad_eta_i[i][m] = values[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m];
1857  }
1858  }
1859 
1860  const double eta_f = values[i_eta_f];
1861 
1862  dealii::Tensor<2, 3> F, C, C_inv;
1863  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1864  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
1865  F[m][n] = values[i_F + m * 3 + n];
1866  C = transpose(F) * F;
1867  C_inv = invert(C);
1868  const dealii::Tensor<1, 3> C_inv_grad_eta = C_inv * grad_eta;
1869  const double grad_eta_C_inv_grad_eta = C_inv_grad_eta * grad_eta;
1870  const double J = determinant(F);
1871 
1872  const double K = D * J / V_m_f;
1873 
1874  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
1875  {
1876  omega = -0.5 * K * grad_eta_C_inv_grad_eta - eta_f * c_f_dot;
1877  }
1878 
1879  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
1880  {
1881  d_omega[i_c_f_dot] = -eta_f;
1882  d_omega[i_eta_f] = -c_f_dot;
1883  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1884  {
1885  d_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m] = -K * C_inv_grad_eta[m];
1886  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
1887  d_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m] = d_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m] * c_i[i]/c_f;
1888  }
1889  }
1890 
1891  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
1892  {
1893  d2_omega = 0.0;
1894 
1895  d2_omega[i_c_f_dot][i_eta_f] = d2_omega[i_eta_f][i_c_f_dot] = -1.0;
1896 
1897  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1898  {
1899  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
1900  {
1901  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m][i_grad_eta_f + n] = -K * C_inv[m][n];
1902  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
1903  {
1904  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m][i_grad_eta_i[i] + n] = d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + n][i_grad_eta_f + m] = -K * C_inv[m][n] * c_i[i]/c_f;
1905  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < I; ++j)
1906  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + n][i_grad_eta_i[j] + m] = -K * C_inv[m][n] * (c_i[i] / c_f) * (c_i[j] / c_f);
1907  }
1908  }
1909  }
1910 
1911  if(compute_dq)
1912  {
1913  const dealii::Tensor<1,3> A = C_inv * grad_eta;
1914  const dealii::Tensor<1,3> F_A = F * A;
1915  const dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_C_inv = F * C_inv;
1916  dealii::Vector<double> F_vect(9), dJ_dF(9);
1917  for(unsigned i = 0; i < 9; ++i)
1918  F_vect[i] = values[i_F + i];
1919  get_dJ_dF(F_vect, dJ_dF);
1920  dealii::Tensor<1,3> C_inv_sum_c_i_c_f_grad_eta_i;
1921  for(unsigned int L = 0; L < 3; ++L)
1922  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
1923  C_inv_sum_c_i_c_f_grad_eta_i[L] += c_i[i]/c_f * grad_eta_i[i][L];
1924  C_inv_sum_c_i_c_f_grad_eta_i = C_inv * C_inv_sum_c_i_c_f_grad_eta_i;
1925 
1926  for(unsigned int L = 0; L < 3; ++L)
1927  {
1928  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1929  {
1930  for(unsigned int M = 0; M < 3; ++M)
1931  {
1932  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + L][i_F + m * 3 + M] = - D / V_m_f * A[L] * dJ_dF[m * 3 + M] + K * (C_inv[L][M] * F_A[m] + A[M] * F_C_inv[m][L] );
1933  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
1934  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + L][i_F + m * 3 + M] = d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + L][i_F + m * 3 + M] * c_i[i] / c_f;
1935  }
1936  }
1937  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + L][i_c_f] = 1.0 / c_f * K * C_inv_sum_c_i_c_f_grad_eta_i[L];
1938  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
1939  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + L][i_c_f] = K * (C_inv_sum_c_i_c_f_grad_eta_i[L] + A[L]) * c_i[i] / c_f / c_f;
1940  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < I; ++j)
1941  {
1942  const dealii::Tensor<1,3> C_inv_grad_eta_j = C_inv * grad_eta_i[j];
1943  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + L][i_c_i[j]] = -K * C_inv_grad_eta_j[L] / c_f;
1944  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
1945  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + L][i_c_i[j]] = -K * C_inv_grad_eta_j[L] * c_i[i] / c_f / c_f;
1946  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[j] + L][i_c_i[j]] += -K * A[L] / c_f;
1947  }
1948  }
1949 
1950  }
1951  }
1952 
1953  return false;
1954 
1955  }
1956 
1957 };

1985 template<unsigned int spacedim>

1995  I;
1996 
1997 public:
1998 
2016  OmegaDualFluidDissipation01(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
2017  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
2018  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
2019  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
2020  const unsigned int I,
2021  const unsigned int method,
2022  const double alpha = 0.0)
2023  :
2024  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 1, 3, 4+3*I, 1+I, method, alpha, "OmegaDualFluidDissipation01"),
2025  I(I)
2026  {
2027  }
2028 
2032  bool
2033  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
2034  const double /*t*/,
2035  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
2036  double& omega,
2037  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
2038  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
2039  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
2040  const bool compute_dq)
2041  const
2042  {
2043 
2044 
2045  // start indices for respective quantities
2046  const unsigned int i_grad_xi_dot = 0;
2047  const unsigned int i_c_f_dot = 3;
2048  const unsigned int i_grad_eta_f = 4;
2049  vector<unsigned int> i_grad_eta_i(I);
2050  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2051  i_grad_eta_i[i] = 7 + 3*i;
2052  const unsigned int i_eta_f = 7 + 3*I;
2053  const unsigned int i_c_f = 8 + 3*I;
2054  vector<unsigned int> i_c_i(I);
2055  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2056  i_c_i[i] = 9 + 3*I + i;
2057 
2058  dealii::Tensor<1,3> grad_xi_dot;
2059  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2060  grad_xi_dot[m] = values[i_grad_xi_dot + m];
2061 
2062  const double c_f_dot = values[i_c_f_dot];
2063  const double c_f = values[i_c_f];
2064  dealii::Vector<double> c_i(I);
2065  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2066  c_i[i] = values[i_c_i[i]];
2067 
2068  dealii::Tensor<1,3> grad_eta;
2069  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2070  grad_eta[m] = values[i_grad_eta_f + m];
2071  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2072  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2073  grad_eta[m] += c_i[i]/c_f * values[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m];
2074 
2075  const double eta_f = values[i_eta_f];
2076 
2077 
2078  const double eps = 0.0;
2079  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
2080  {
2081  omega = grad_xi_dot * grad_eta - eta_f * c_f_dot + grad_xi_dot * grad_xi_dot * 0.5 * eps;
2082  }
2083 
2084  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
2085  {
2086  d_omega[i_c_f_dot] = -eta_f;
2087  d_omega[i_eta_f] = -c_f_dot;
2088  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2089  {
2090  d_omega[i_grad_xi_dot + m] = grad_eta[m];
2091  d_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m] = grad_xi_dot[m];
2092  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2093  d_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m] = grad_xi_dot[m] * c_i[i]/c_f;
2094  d_omega[i_grad_xi_dot + m] += grad_xi_dot[m] * eps;
2095  }
2096  }
2097 
2098  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
2099  {
2100  d2_omega[i_c_f_dot][i_eta_f] = d2_omega[i_eta_f][i_c_f_dot] = -1.0;
2101 
2102  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2103  {
2104  d2_omega[i_grad_xi_dot + m][i_grad_eta_f + m] = d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m][i_grad_xi_dot + m] = 1.0;
2105  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2106  d2_omega[i_grad_xi_dot + m][i_grad_eta_i[i] + m] = d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m][i_grad_xi_dot + m] = c_i[i]/c_f;
2107  }
2108 
2109  if(compute_dq)
2110  {
2111  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2112  {
2113  d2_omega[i_grad_xi_dot + m][i_c_f] = (values[i_grad_eta_f + m] - grad_eta[m]) / c_f;
2114  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2115  d2_omega[i_grad_xi_dot + m][i_c_i[i]] = values[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m] / c_f;
2116  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2117  {
2118  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m][i_c_f] = -grad_xi_dot[m] * c_i[i]/c_f/c_f;
2119  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m][i_c_i[i]] = grad_xi_dot[m] * 1.0/c_f;
2120  }
2121  }
2122 
2123  }
2124 
2125  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2126  {
2127  d2_omega(i_grad_xi_dot + m, i_grad_xi_dot + m) += eps;
2128  }
2129 
2130  }
2131 
2132  return false;
2133 
2134  }
2135 };

2257  const

2260  (void)compute_dq;
2261  Assert(!compute_dq, dealii::ExcMessage("The alpha-family for temporal discretization is not currently implemented!"));
2262 
2263  // start indices for respective quantities
2264  const unsigned int i_F_dot = 0;
2265  const unsigned int i_grad_eta_f = 9;
2266  vector<unsigned int> i_grad_eta_i(I);
2267  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2268  i_grad_eta_i[i] = 12 + 3*i;
2269  const unsigned int i_eta_f = 12 + 3*I;
2270  vector<unsigned int> i_c_i(I);
2271  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2272  i_c_i[i] = 13 + 3*I + i;
2273  const unsigned int i_F = 13 + 4*I;
2274 
2275  dealii::Tensor<2, 3> F_dot, F;
2276  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2277  {
2278  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
2279  {
2280  F_dot[m][n] = values [i_F_dot + m * 3 + n];
2281  F[m][n] = values [i_F + m * 3 + n];
2282  }
2283  }
2284  dealii::Vector<double> c_i(I);
2285  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2286  c_i[i] = values[i_c_i[i]];
2287  const double J =determinant(F);
2288  const double c_f = (J - n_0) / V_m_f;
2289 
2290  dealii::Tensor<1,3> grad_eta;
2291  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2292  grad_eta[m] = values[i_grad_eta_f + m];
2293  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2294  {
2295  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2296  {
2297  grad_eta[m] += c_i[i]/c_f * values[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m];
2298  }
2299  }
2300 
2301  const double eta_f = values[i_eta_f];
2302 
2303  dealii::Tensor<2, 3> F_inv, C_inv;
2304  F_inv = invert(F);
2305  C_inv = F_inv * transpose(F_inv);
2306  const dealii::Tensor<1, 3> C_inv_grad_eta = C_inv * grad_eta;
2307  const double grad_eta_C_inv_grad_eta = C_inv_grad_eta * grad_eta;
2308

2310 
2311  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
2312  {
2313  omega = -0.5 * K * grad_eta_C_inv_grad_eta - eta_f * J * scalar_product(F_inv, transpose(F_dot)) / V_m_f;
2314  }
2315 
2316  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
2317  {
2318  d_omega = 0.0;
2319  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2320  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
2321  d_omega[i_F_dot + m * 3 + n] = -eta_f * J / V_m_f * F_inv[n][m];
2322  d_omega[i_eta_f] = -J * scalar_product(F_inv, transpose(F_dot)) / V_m_f;
2323  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2324  {
2325  d_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m] = -K * C_inv_grad_eta[m];
2326  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2327  d_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m] = d_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m] * c_i[i]/c_f;
2328  }
2329  }
2330 
2331  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
2332  {

2334  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)

2336  d2_omega[i_F_dot + m * 3 + n][i_eta_f] = d2_omega[i_eta_f][i_F_dot + m * 3 + n] = -J / V_m_f * F_inv[n][m];
2337 
2338  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2339  {
2340  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
2341  {
2342  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m][i_grad_eta_f + n] = -K * C_inv[m][n];
2343  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2344  {
2345  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m][i_grad_eta_i[i] + n] = d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + n][i_grad_eta_f + m] = -K * C_inv[m][n] * c_i[i]/c_f;
2346  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < I; ++j)
2347  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + n][i_grad_eta_i[j] + m] = -K * C_inv[m][n] * (c_i[i] / c_f) * (c_i[j] / c_f);
2348  }

2350  }

2491

2493  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)

2496  {
2497  F_dot[m][n] = values [i_F_dot + m * 3 + n];
2498  F[m][n] = values [i_F + m * 3 + n];
2499  }
2500  }

2524  }

2527  {
2528  d_omega = 0.0;

2532  d_omega[i_F_dot + m * 3 + n] = -eta_f * J / V_m_f * F_inv[n][m];
2533  d_omega[i_eta_f] = -J * scalar_product(F_inv, transpose(F_dot)) / V_m_f;
2534  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2535  {
2536  d_omega[i_grad_xi_dot + m] = grad_eta[m];
2537  d_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m] = grad_xi_dot[m];

2540  }

2549

2551  {
2552  d2_omega[i_grad_xi_dot + m][i_grad_eta_f + m] = d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m][i_grad_xi_dot + m] = 1.0;

2555  }
2556  }

2669  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2670  grad_xi_dot[m] = values[i_grad_xi_dot + m];
2671 
2672  const double c_f_dot = values[i_c_f_dot];
2673 
2674  dealii::Tensor<1,3> u_dot;
2675  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2676  u_dot[m] = values[i_u_dot + m];

2695  grad_eta_f[m] = values[i_grad_eta_f + m];

2700  {

2702  grad_eta_i[i][m] = values[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m];
2703  }
2704  }

2708  std::vector<dealii::Tensor<1,3>> C_inv_grad_eta_i(I), F_inv_grad_eta_i(I);
2709  F_inv = invert(F);
2710  C_inv = F_inv * transpose(F_inv);
2711  C_inv_grad_xi_dot = C_inv * grad_xi_dot;
2712  grad_xi_dot_F_inv = transpose(F_inv) * grad_xi_dot;

2723  }

2752  {

2754  d2_omega(i_u_dot + m, i_grad_eta_f + n) = d2_omega(i_grad_eta_f + n, i_u_dot + m) = -F_inv[n][m] * c_f;

3205  if(is_active)
3206  {
3207  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
3208  {
3209  if(delta_eta >= eta_c)
3210  sigma = -1.0 / (2.0 * R) * (delta_eta - eta_c) * (delta_eta - eta_c);
3211  else
3212  sigma = 0.0;
3213  }
3214 
3215  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
3216  {
3217  if(delta_eta >= eta_c)
3218  d_sigma[0] = -1.0 / R * (delta_eta - eta_c);
3219  else
3220  d_sigma = 0.0;
3221  }
3222 
3223  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
3224  {
3225  if(delta_eta >= eta_c)
3226  d2_sigma[0][0] = -1.0 / R;
3227  else
3228  // small second derivative to ensure definiteness of system
3229  d2_sigma[0][0] = -regularization / R;
3230  }
3231  }
3232 
3233  return false;
3234  }
3235 
3236 };

3256 template<unsigned int spacedim>
3257 class OmegaElectrolysis01 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
3258 {
3259 private:
3260 
3264  const double
3265  F;
3266 
3270  const double
3271  RT;
3272 
3276  const double
3277  A_e;
3278 
3282  dealii::Function<spacedim>&
3283  phi_bar;
3284 
3288  const double
3289  i_0;
3290 
3294  const double
3295  R_el;
3296 
3297 public:
3298 
3327  OmegaElectrolysis01(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_sigma,
3328  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
3329  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
3330  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
3331  const double F,
3332  const double RT,
3333  const double A_e,
3334  dealii::Function<spacedim>& phi_bar,
3335  const double i_0,
3336  const double R_el,
3337  const unsigned int method,
3338  const double alpha = 0.0)
3339  :
3340  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_sigma, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 0, 0, 1, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaElectrolysis01"),
3341  F(F),
3342  RT(RT),
3343  A_e(A_e),
3344  phi_bar(phi_bar),
3345  i_0(i_0),
3346  R_el(R_el)
3347  {
3348  }
3349 
3353  bool
3354  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
3355  const double t,
3356  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& x,
3357  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& /*n*/,
3358  double& sigma,
3359  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
3360  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
3361  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
3362  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
3363  const
3364  {
3365 
3366  const double time_old = phi_bar.get_time();
3367  phi_bar.set_time(t);
3368  const double eta_bar_ = -A_e * F * phi_bar.value(x);
3369  phi_bar.set_time(time_old);
3370 
3371  const double eta_int = values[0];
3372  const double delta_eta = eta_int + eta_bar_;
3373 
3374  // iterate for corresponding current
3375  double I_k = 0.0;
3376  double f_old = 1e16;
3377  unsigned int iter = 0;
3378  for(;;)
3379  {
3380  iter++;
3381  const double f = asinh(I_k * F / i_0) + 1.0 / RT * R_el * F * F * I_k + delta_eta / RT;
3382  if(fabs(fabs(f) - fabs(f_old)) < 1e-16)
3383  break;
3384  if(iter == 100)
3385  return true;
3386  f_old = f;
3387  const double df_dI_k = (F / i_0) / sqrt( 1.0 + (I_k * F / i_0) * (I_k * F / i_0) ) + 1.0 / RT * R_el * F * F;
3388  const double dI_k = - f / df_dI_k;
3389  I_k = I_k + dI_k;
3390  }
3391 
3392  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
3393  sigma = delta_eta * I_k - i_0 * RT / F * ( sqrt( 1.0 + (I_k * F / i_0) * (I_k * F / i_0) ) - 1.0 ) + RT * I_k * asinh(I_k * F / i_0) + 0.5 * R_el * (I_k * F) * (I_k * F);
3394 
3395  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
3396  d_sigma[0] = I_k;
3397 
3398  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
3399  {
3400  d2_sigma[0][0] = -1.0 / (RT * F / i_0 / sqrt( 1.0 + (I_k * F / i_0) * (I_k * F / i_0) ) + R_el * F * F);
3401  }
3402 
3403  return false;
3404  }
3405 
3406 };

3568  dB_dQ(3,0) = Q[5]; dB_dQ(3,1) = 0; dB_dQ(3,2) = -2.0*Q[2]; dB_dQ(3,3) = 0; dB_dQ(3,4) = 0; dB_dQ(3,5) = Q[0];
3569  dB_dQ(4,0) = -Q[4]; dB_dQ(4,1) = Q[2]; dB_dQ(4,2) = Q[1]; dB_dQ(4,3) = 0; dB_dQ(4,4) = -Q[0]; dB_dQ(4,5) = 0;
3570  dB_dQ(5,0) = Q[3]; dB_dQ(5,1) = -2.0*Q[1]; dB_dQ(5,2) = 0; dB_dQ(5,3) = Q[0]; dB_dQ(5,4) = 0; dB_dQ(5,5) = 0;
3571 
3572  const double detQ = get_J(Q, true);
3573  get_dJ_dF(Q, ddetQ_dQ, true);
3574  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 6; ++i)
3575  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 6; ++j)
3576  dQ_inv_dQ(i,j) = ( dB_dQ(i,j) - B[i] * ddetQ_dQ[j] / detQ ) / detQ;
3577 
3578  }
3579 
3580  const double dd = d * d;
3581  const double dd_n = dd > 0.0 ? pow(dd, n) : 0.0;
3582  const double dd_n_1 = dd > 0.0 ? pow(dd, n-1.0) : 0.0;
3583  const double dd_n_2 = dd > 0.0 ? pow(dd, n-2.0) : 0.0;
3584 
3585  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
3586  {
3587  omega = 0.5 * A/n * dd_n;
3588  }
3589 
3590  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
3591  {
3592  dealii::Vector<double> d_dd_dQ_dot(6);
3593  dd_dQ_dot.Tvmult(d_dd_dQ_dot, d);
3594  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 6; ++m)
3595  d_omega[m] = A * dd_n_1 * d_dd_dQ_dot[m];
3596  }
3597 
3598  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
3599  {
3600  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 9; ++i)
3601  {
3602  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 9; ++j)
3603  d2delta_dd2(i,j) = 2.0 * A * (n - 1.0) * dd_n_2 * d[i] * d[j];
3604  d2delta_dd2(i,i) += A * dd_n_1;
3605  }
3606  d2delta_dd2.mmult(d2delta_dd2_dd_dQ_dot, dd_dQ_dot);
3607  dd_dQ_dot.Tmmult(dd_dQ_dot_d2delta_dd2_dd_dQ_dot, d2delta_dd2_dd_dQ_dot);
3608  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 6; ++i)
3609  {
3610  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 6; ++j)
3611  d2_omega(i,j) = dd_dQ_dot_d2delta_dd2_dd_dQ_dot(i,j);
3612  }
3613 
3614  if(compute_dq)
3615  {
3616  d2delta_dd2_dd_dQ_dot.Tmmult(d2delta_dd2_dd_dQ_dot_T_dd_dQ_inv, dd_dQ_inv);
3617  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 6; ++i)
3618  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 6; ++j)
3619  d2delta_dQ_dot_dQ_inv(i,j) = d2delta_dd2_dd_dQ_dot_T_dd_dQ_inv(i,j) + A * dd_n_1 * d_d2d_dQ_dot_d_Q_inv(i,j);
3620  d2delta_dQ_dot_dQ_inv.mmult(d2delta_dQ_dot_dQ, dQ_inv_dQ);
3621  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 6; ++i)
3622  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 6; ++j)
3623  d2_omega(i,j + 6) = d2delta_dQ_dot_dQ(i,j);
3624  }
3625 
3626  }
3627 
3628  return false;
3629  }
3630 
3631 };

3799  const double dd = d * d;
3800  const double sqrt_dd = sqrt(dd);
3801  const double A_0 = A * pow(d_th, 2.0 * (n - 1.0));
3802  const double h = sqrt_dd > d_th ? A / n * pow(dd, n) : A_0 * dd;
3803  const double dh = sqrt_dd > d_th ? A * pow(dd, n - 1.0) : A_0;
3804  const double d2h = sqrt_dd > d_th ? A * (n - 1.0) * pow(dd, n - 2.0) : 0.0;

3825  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 9; ++j)

3925  dF_inv_dF(7,7) = -F[0]*F[0]*F[4]*F[8] + F[0]*F[1]*F[3]*F[8] + F[0]*F[2]*F[4]*F[6] - F[1]*F[2]*F[3]*F[6];
3926  dF_inv_dF(7,8) = F[0]*F[0]*F[4]*F[7] - F[0]*F[1]*F[3]*F[7] - F[0]*F[1]*F[4]*F[6] + F[1]*F[1]*F[3]*F[6];
3927  dF_inv_dF(8,0) = -F[1]*F[3]*F[5]*F[7] + F[1]*F[4]*F[5]*F[6] + F[2]*F[3]*F[4]*F[7] - F[2]*F[4]*F[4]*F[6];
3928  dF_inv_dF(8,1) = F[0]*F[3]*F[5]*F[7] - F[0]*F[4]*F[5]*F[6] - F[2]*F[3]*F[3]*F[7] + F[2]*F[3]*F[4]*F[6];
3929  dF_inv_dF(8,2) = -F[0]*F[3]*F[4]*F[7] + F[0]*F[4]*F[4]*F[6] + F[1]*F[3]*F[3]*F[7] - F[1]*F[3]*F[4]*F[6];
3930  dF_inv_dF(8,3) = F[0]*F[1]*F[5]*F[7] - F[0]*F[2]*F[4]*F[7] - F[1]*F[1]*F[5]*F[6] + F[1]*F[2]*F[4]*F[6];
3931  dF_inv_dF(8,4) = -F[0]*F[0]*F[5]*F[7] + F[0]*F[1]*F[5]*F[6] + F[0]*F[2]*F[3]*F[7] - F[1]*F[2]*F[3]*F[6];
3932  dF_inv_dF(8,5) = F[0]*F[0]*F[4]*F[7] - F[0]*F[1]*F[3]*F[7] - F[0]*F[1]*F[4]*F[6] + F[1]*F[1]*F[3]*F[6];
3933  dF_inv_dF(8,6) = -F[0]*F[1]*F[4]*F[5] + F[0]*F[2]*F[4]*F[4] + F[1]*F[1]*F[3]*F[5] - F[1]*F[2]*F[3]*F[4];
3934  dF_inv_dF(8,7) = F[0]*F[0]*F[4]*F[5] - F[0]*F[1]*F[3]*F[5] - F[0]*F[2]*F[3]*F[4] + F[1]*F[2]*F[3]*F[3];
3935  dF_inv_dF(8,8) = -F[0]*F[0]*F[4]*F[4] + 2.0*F[0]*F[1]*F[3]*F[4] - F[1]*F[1]*F[3]*F[3];
3936  dF_inv_dF *= 1.0/get_J(F)/get_J(F);
3937 
3938  dd_dF_inv.Tvmult(d_dd_dF_inv, d);
3939  dd_dF_dot.Tmmult(d2delta_dF_dot_dF_inv, dd_dF_inv);
3940  d2delta_dF_dot_dF_inv *= dh;
3941  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 9; ++i)
3942  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 9; ++j)
3943  d2delta_dF_dot_dF_inv(i,j) += 2.0 * d2h * d_dd_dF_dot[i] * d_dd_dF_inv[j] + dh * d_d2d_dF_dot_d_F_inv(i,j);
3944  d2delta_dF_dot_dF_inv.mmult(d2delta_dF_dot_dF, dF_inv_dF);
3945  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 9; ++i)
3946  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 9; ++j)
3947  d2_omega(i,j + 9) = d2delta_dF_dot_dF(i,j);
3948  }
3949 
3950  }
3951 
3952  return false;
3953  }
3954 
3958  double
3959  get_maximum_step( const dealii::Vector<double>& e_omega,
3960  const std::vector<dealii::Vector<double>>& /*e_omega_ref_sets*/,
3961  const dealii::Vector<double>& delta_e_omega,
3962  const dealii::Vector<double>& /*hidden_vars*/,
3963  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/)
3964  const
3965  {
3966 
3967  double factor = 2.0;
3968  static dealii::Vector<double> F(9);
3969  while(true)
3970  {
3971 
3972  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 9; ++m)
3973  F[m] = e_omega[m] + factor * delta_e_omega[m];
3974  if( (get_J(F) > 0.0) )
3975  break;
3976 
3977  factor *= 0.5;
3978  Assert(factor > 0.0, dealii::ExcMessage("Cannot determine a positive scaling of the load step such that the determinant of the deformation gradient and that of Q stays positive!"));
3979  }
3980  return factor;
3981  }
3982 
3983 };

4023 class OmegaVelocityFlux00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
4024 {
4025 
4026 public:
4027 
4043  OmegaVelocityFlux00(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
4044  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,

4053 
4057  bool
4058  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
4059  const double /*t*/,
4060  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
4061  double& omega,
4062  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
4063  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
4064  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
4065  const bool compute_dq)
4066  const
4067  {
4068 
4069  (void)compute_dq;
4070  Assert(!compute_dq, dealii::ExcMessage("The alpha-family for temporal discretization is not currently implemented!"));
4071 
4072  // start indices for respective quantities
4073  const unsigned int i_u_dot = 0;
4074  const unsigned int i_v = 3;
4075  const unsigned int i_I = 6;
4076  const unsigned int i_t = 9;
4077  const unsigned int i_c = 12;
4078  const unsigned int i_F = 13;
4079 
4080  dealii::Tensor<1,3> u_dot, v, I, t_;
4081  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F;
4082  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
4083  {
4084  u_dot[i] = values[i_u_dot + i];
4085  v[i] = values[i_v + i];
4086  I[i] = values[i_I + i];
4087  t_[i] = values[i_t + i];
4088  }
4089  const double c = values[i_c];
4090  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
4091  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 3; ++j)
4092  F[i][j] = values[i_F + i * 3 + j];
4093 
4094  dealii::Tensor<1,3> c_F_I = 1.0/c * F * I;
4095  dealii::Tensor<1,3> c_t_F = 1.0/c * transpose(F) * t_;
4096 
4097  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
4098  {
4099  omega = t_ * (v - u_dot - c_F_I);
4100  }
4101 
4102  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
4103  {
4104  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
4105  {
4106  d_omega[i_u_dot + i] = -t_[i];
4107  d_omega[i_v + i] = t_[i];
4108  d_omega[i_I + i] = -c_t_F[i];
4109  d_omega[i_t + i] = (v - u_dot - c_F_I)[i];
4110  }
4111  }
4112 
4113  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
4114  {
4115  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
4116  {
4117  d2_omega[i_u_dot + i][i_t + i] = d2_omega[i_t + i][i_u_dot + i] = -1.0;
4118  d2_omega[i_v + i][i_t + i] = d2_omega[i_t + i][i_v + i] = 1.0;
4119  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 3; ++j)
4120  d2_omega[i_I + i][i_t + j] = d2_omega[i_t + j][i_I + i] = -1.0 / c * F[j][i];
4121  }
4122  }
4123 
4124  return false;
4125 
4126  }

4291

4294  }

4334 template<unsigned int spacedim>
4335 class OmegaViscousDissipation02 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
4336 {
4337 
4338 private:
4339 
4343  const double
4344  eta;
4345 
4346 public:
4347 
4365  OmegaViscousDissipation02( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
4366  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
4367  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
4368  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
4369  const double eta,
4370  const unsigned int method,
4371  const double alpha = 0.0)
4372  :
4373  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 0, 9, 0, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaViscousDissipation02"),
4374  eta(eta)
4375  {
4376  }
4377 
4381  bool
4382  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
4383  const double /*t*/,
4384  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
4385  double& omega,
4386  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
4387  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
4388  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
4389  const bool compute_dq)
4390  const
4391  {
4392 
4393  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_ref_v, F, F_inv, C_inv, grad_v, delta;
4394  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4395  {
4396  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
4397  {
4398  grad_ref_v[r][S] = values[3 * r + S];
4399  F[r][S] = values[9 + 3 * r + S];
4400  }
4401  }
4402  F_inv = invert(F);
4403  C_inv = F_inv * transpose(F_inv);
4404  grad_v = grad_ref_v * F_inv;
4405  delta[0][0] = delta[1][1] = delta[2][2] = 1.0;
4406  const double J = determinant(F);
4407 
4408  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
4409  {
4410  omega = 0.5 * J * eta * ( trace(grad_v * transpose(grad_v)) + trace(grad_v * grad_v) );
4411  }
4412 
4413  dealii::Tensor<2,3> T;
4414  if(get<1>(requested_quantities) || get<2>(requested_quantities))
4415  {
4416  T = J * eta * (grad_v + transpose(grad_v)) * transpose(F_inv);
4417  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
4418  {
4419  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4420  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
4421  d_omega[r * 3 + S] = T[r][S];
4422  }
4423  }
4424 
4425  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
4426  {
4427  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4428  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
4429  for(unsigned int p = 0; p < 3; ++p)
4430  for(unsigned int Q = 0; Q < 3; ++Q)
4431  d2_omega(r * 3 + S, p * 3 + Q) = J * eta * (delta[r][p] * C_inv[S][Q] + F_inv[Q][r] * F_inv[S][p]);
4432  if(compute_dq)
4433  {
4434  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv_grad_v, F_inv_grad_v_T;
4435  F_inv_grad_v = F_inv * grad_v;
4436  F_inv_grad_v_T = F_inv * transpose(grad_v);
4437 
4438  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4439  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
4440  for(unsigned int p = 0; p < 3; ++p)
4441  for(unsigned int Q = 0; Q < 3; ++Q)
4442  d2_omega(r * 3 + S, p * 3 + Q + 9) = F_inv[Q][p] * T[r][S] - J * eta * ( F_inv_grad_v[S][p] * F_inv[Q][r] + C_inv[Q][S] * grad_v[r][p] + ( F_inv_grad_v[Q][r] + F_inv_grad_v_T[Q][r] ) * F_inv[S][p] );
4443  }
4444  }
4445 
4446  return false;
4447  }
4448 };

4481 template<unsigned int spacedim>
4482 class OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
4483 {
4484 
4485 public:
4486 
4502  OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
4503  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
4504  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
4505  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
4506  const unsigned int method,
4507  const double alpha = 0.0)
4508  :
4509  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 1, 0, 9, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility00")
4510  {
4511  }
4512 
4516  bool
4517  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
4518  const double /*t*/,
4519  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
4520  double& omega,
4521  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
4522  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
4523  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
4524  const bool compute_dq)
4525  const
4526  {
4527 
4528  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_ref_f, F, F_inv, grad_f;
4529 
4530  const double xi_dot = values[0];
4531  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4532  {
4533  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
4534  {
4535  grad_ref_f[r][S] = values[1 + 3 * r + S];
4536  F[r][S] = values[1 + 9 + 3 * r + S];
4537  }
4538  }
4539  F_inv = invert(F);
4540  grad_f = grad_ref_f * F_inv;
4541  const double J = determinant(F);
4542  const double tr_grad_f = trace(grad_f);
4543 
4544  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
4545  {
4546  omega = -J * tr_grad_f * xi_dot;
4547  }
4548 
4549  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
4550  {
4551  d_omega[0] = -J *tr_grad_f;
4552  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4553  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4554  d_omega[1 + r * 3 + R] = -J * F_inv[R][r] * xi_dot;
4555  }
4556 
4557  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
4558  {
4559  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4560  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4561  d2_omega(0, 1 + r * 3 + R) = d2_omega(1 + r * 3 + R, 0) = -J * F_inv[R][r];
4562 
4563  if(compute_dq)
4564  {
4565  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv_grad_f = F_inv * grad_f;
4566  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4567  {
4568  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4569  {
4570  d2_omega(0, 1 + 9 + r * 3 + R) = -J * ( tr_grad_f * F_inv[R][r] - F_inv_grad_f[R][r]);
4571  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
4572  for(unsigned int K = 0; K < 3; ++K)
4573  d2_omega(1 + k * 3 + K, 1 + 9 + r * 3 + R) = -J * xi_dot * ( F_inv[R][r] * F_inv[K][k] - F_inv[K][r] * F_inv[R][k] );
4574  }
4575  }
4576  }
4577  }
4578 
4579  return false;
4580  }

4610 template<unsigned int spacedim>
4611 class OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility01 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
4612 {
4613 
4614 public:
4615 
4631  OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility01( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
4632  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
4633  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
4634  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
4635  const unsigned int method,
4636  const double alpha = 0.0)
4637  :
4638  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 3, 0, 3, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility01")
4639  {
4640  }
4641 
4645  bool
4646  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
4647  const double /*t*/,
4648  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
4649  double& omega,
4650  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
4651  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
4652  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
4653  const bool compute_dq)
4654  const
4655  {
4656 
4657  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F, F_inv;
4658  dealii::Tensor<1,3> grad_xi_dot_ref, f_def, f_ref, grad_xi_dot_def;
4659 
4660  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4661  {
4662  grad_xi_dot_ref[r] = values[r];
4663  f_def[r] = values[3 + r];
4664  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
4665  F[r][S] = values[6 + 3 * r + S];
4666  }
4667  F_inv = invert(F);
4668  const double J = determinant(F);
4669 
4670  f_ref = J * F_inv * f_def;
4671  grad_xi_dot_def = J * transpose(F_inv) * grad_xi_dot_ref;
4672 
4673  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
4674  {
4675  omega = f_ref * grad_xi_dot_ref;
4676  }
4677 
4678  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
4679  {
4680  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4681  {
4682  d_omega[r] = f_ref[r];
4683  d_omega[r + 3] = grad_xi_dot_def[r];
4684  }
4685  }
4686 
4687  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
4688  {
4689  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4690  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4691  d2_omega(R, 3 + r) = d2_omega(3 + r, R) = J * F_inv[R][r];
4692 
4693  if(compute_dq)
4694  {
4695  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
4696  {
4697  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4698  {
4699  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4700  {
4701  d2_omega(k, 6 + 3 * r + R) = F_inv[R][r] * f_ref[k] - F_inv[k][r] * f_ref[R];
4702  d2_omega(k + 3, 6 + 3 * r + R) = F_inv[R][r] * grad_xi_dot_def[k] - F_inv[R][k] * grad_xi_dot_def[r];
4703  }
4704  }
4705  }
4706  }
4707  }
4708 
4709  return false;
4710  }
4711 };

4738 template<unsigned int spacedim>
4739 class OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility02 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
4740 {
4741 private:
4742 
4746  const bool
4747  flip_normal;
4748 
4749 public:
4750 
4768  OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility02( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_omega,
4769  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
4770  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
4771  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
4772  const bool flip_normal,
4773  const unsigned int method,
4774  const double alpha = 0.0)
4775  :
4776  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 1, 0, 3, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility02"),
4777  flip_normal(flip_normal)
4778  {
4779  }
4780 
4784  bool
4785  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
4786  const double /*t*/,
4787  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
4788  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& n,
4789  double& sigma,
4790  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
4791  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
4792  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
4793  const bool compute_dq)
4794  const
4795  {
4796 
4797  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F, F_inv;
4798 
4799  const double xi_dot = values[0];
4800  dealii::Tensor<1,3> f;
4801  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4802  {
4803  f[r] = values[1 + r];
4804  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
4805  F[r][S] = values[4 + 3 * r + S];
4806  }
4807  F_inv = invert(F);
4808  const double J = determinant(F);
4809 
4810  dealii::Tensor<1, 3> n__, n_;
4811  n__[0] = n[0];
4812  n__[1] = spacedim < 2 ? 0.0 : n[1];
4813  n__[2] = spacedim < 3 ? 0.0 : n[2];
4814  n_ = flip_normal ? -J * transpose(F_inv) * n__ : J * transpose(F_inv) * n__;
4815 
4816  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
4817  {
4818  sigma = xi_dot * f * n_;
4819  }
4820 
4821  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
4822  {
4823  d_sigma[0] = f * n_;
4824  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4825  d_sigma[1 + r] = xi_dot * n_[r];
4826  }
4827 
4828  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
4829  {
4830 
4831  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4832  d2_sigma(0, 1 + r) = d2_sigma(1 + r, 0) = n_[r];
4833 
4834  if(compute_dq)
4835  {
4836  dealii::Tensor<3,3> dn_dF;
4837  dealii::Tensor<2,3> f_dn_dF;
4838  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
4839  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4840  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4841  dn_dF[m][r][R] = F_inv[R][r] * n_[m] - F_inv[R][m] * n_[r];
4842  f_dn_dF = f * dn_dF;
4843  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4844  {
4845  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4846  {
4847  d2_sigma(0, 4 + r * 3 + R) = f_dn_dF[r][R];
4848  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
4849  d2_sigma(1 + k, 4 + r * 3 + R) = xi_dot * dn_dF[k][r][R];
4850  }
4851  }
4852  }
4853  }
4854 
4855  return false;
4856  }
4857 };

4890 template<unsigned int spacedim>
4891 class OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility03 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
4892 {
4893 
4894 public:
4895 
4911  OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility03( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_omega,
4912  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
4913  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
4914  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
4915  const unsigned int method,
4916  const double alpha = 0.0)
4917  :
4918  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 1, 0, 9, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility03")
4919  {
4920  }
4921 
4925  bool
4926  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
4927  const double /*t*/,
4928  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
4929  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& /*n*/,
4930  double& sigma,
4931  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
4932  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
4933  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
4934  const bool compute_dq)
4935  const
4936  {
4937 
4938  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_ref_f, F, F_inv, grad_f;
4939 
4940  const double xi_dot = values[0];
4941  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4942  {
4943  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
4944  {
4945  grad_ref_f[r][S] = values[1 + 3 * r + S];
4946  F[r][S] = values[1 + 9 + 3 * r + S];
4947  }
4948  }
4949  F_inv = invert(F);
4950  grad_f = grad_ref_f * F_inv;
4951  const double J = determinant(F);
4952  const double tr_grad_f = trace(grad_f);
4953 
4954  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
4955  {
4956  sigma = -J * tr_grad_f * xi_dot;
4957  }
4958 
4959  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
4960  {
4961  d_sigma[0] = -J *tr_grad_f;
4962  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4963  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4964  d_sigma[1 + r * 3 + R] = -J * F_inv[R][r] * xi_dot;
4965  }
4966 
4967  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
4968  {
4969  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4970  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4971  d2_sigma(0, 1 + r * 3 + R) = d2_sigma(1 + r * 3 + R, 0) = -J * F_inv[R][r];
4972 
4973  if(compute_dq)
4974  {
4975  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv_grad_f = F_inv * grad_f;
4976  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4977  {
4978  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4979  {
4980  d2_sigma(0, 1 + 9 + r * 3 + R) = -J * ( tr_grad_f * F_inv[R][r] - F_inv_grad_f[R][r]);
4981  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
4982  for(unsigned int K = 0; K < 3; ++K)
4983  d2_sigma(1 + k * 3 + K, 1 + 9 + r * 3 + R) = -J * xi_dot * ( F_inv[R][r] * F_inv[K][k] - F_inv[K][r] * F_inv[R][k] );
4984  }
4985  }
4986  }
4987  }
4988 
4989  return false;
4990  }

5021 template<unsigned int spacedim>
5022 class OmegaFluidIncompressibility00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
5023 {
5024 
5025 private:
5026 
5030  const double
5031  V_m_f;
5032 
5033 public:
5034 
5052  OmegaFluidIncompressibility00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
5053  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
5054  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
5055  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
5056  const double V_m_f,
5057  const unsigned int method,
5058  const double alpha = 0.0)
5059  :
5060  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 4, 3, 4, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaDualFluidIncompressibility00"),
5061  V_m_f(V_m_f)
5062  {
5063  }
5064 
5068  bool
5069  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
5070  const double /*t*/,
5071  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
5072  double& omega,
5073  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
5074  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
5075  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
5076  const bool compute_dq)
5077  const
5078  {
5079 
5080  // start indices for respective quantities
5081  const unsigned int i_v_dot = 0;
5082  const unsigned int i_c_f_dot = 3;
5083  const unsigned int i_u_dot = 4;
5084  const unsigned int i_grad_eta_f = 7;
5085  const unsigned int i_eta_f = 10;
5086  const unsigned int i_F = 11;
5087 
5088  dealii::Tensor<1,3> v_dot;
5089  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5090  v_dot[m] = values[i_v_dot + m];
5091 
5092  const double c_f_dot = values[i_c_f_dot];
5093 
5094  dealii::Tensor<1,3> u_dot;
5095  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5096  u_dot[m] = values[i_u_dot + m];
5097 
5098  const double eta_f = values[i_eta_f];
5099 
5100  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F;
5101  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5102  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
5103  F[m][n] = values[i_F + m * 3 + n];
5104  const double J = determinant(F);
5105  const double c_f = J / V_m_f;
5106 
5107  dealii::Tensor<1,3> grad_eta_c_f, grad_eta_f;
5108  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5109  {
5110  grad_eta_c_f[m] = c_f * values[i_grad_eta_f + m];
5111  grad_eta_f[m] = values[i_grad_eta_f + m];
5112  }
5113 
5114  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv;
5115  dealii::Tensor<1,3> F_inv_delta_v_dot, grad_eta_f_F_inv, grad_eta_c_f_F_inv, delta_v_dot;
5116  F_inv = invert(F);
5117  delta_v_dot = v_dot - u_dot;
5118  F_inv_delta_v_dot = F_inv * delta_v_dot;
5119  grad_eta_f_F_inv = transpose(F_inv) * grad_eta_f;
5120  grad_eta_c_f_F_inv = transpose(F_inv) * grad_eta_c_f;
5121 
5122  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
5123  {
5124  omega = F_inv_delta_v_dot * grad_eta_c_f - eta_f * c_f_dot;
5125  }
5126 
5127  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
5128  {
5129  d_omega[i_c_f_dot] = -eta_f;
5130  d_omega[i_eta_f] = -c_f_dot;
5131  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5132  {
5133  d_omega[i_v_dot + m] = grad_eta_c_f_F_inv[m];
5134  d_omega[i_u_dot + m] = -grad_eta_c_f_F_inv[m];
5135  d_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m] = F_inv_delta_v_dot[m] * c_f;
5136  }
5137  }
5138 
5139  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
5140  {
5141 
5142  d2_omega[i_c_f_dot][i_eta_f] = d2_omega[i_eta_f][i_c_f_dot] = -1.0;
5143 
5144  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5145  {
5146  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
5147  {
5148  d2_omega(i_v_dot + m, i_grad_eta_f + n) = d2_omega(i_grad_eta_f + n, i_v_dot + m) = F_inv[n][m] * c_f;
5149  d2_omega(i_u_dot + m, i_grad_eta_f + n) = d2_omega(i_grad_eta_f + n, i_u_dot + m) = -F_inv[n][m] * c_f;
5150  }
5151  }
5152 
5153 
5154  if(compute_dq)
5155  {
5156  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5157  {
5158  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
5159  {
5160  for(unsigned int l = 0; l < 3; ++l)
5161  {
5162  d2_omega(i_v_dot + m, i_F + 3 * k + l) = -grad_eta_c_f_F_inv[k] * F_inv[l][m] + grad_eta_c_f_F_inv[m] * F_inv[l][k];
5163  d2_omega(i_u_dot + m, i_F + 3 * k + l) = grad_eta_c_f_F_inv[k] * F_inv[l][m] - grad_eta_c_f_F_inv[m] * F_inv[l][k];
5164  d2_omega(i_grad_eta_f + m, i_F + 3 * k + l) = -F_inv_delta_v_dot[l] * F_inv[m][k] * c_f + F_inv_delta_v_dot[m] * c_f * F_inv[l][k];
5165  }
5166  }
5167 
5168  }
5169 
5170  }
5171 
5172  }
5173  return false;
5174 
5175  }

5214 template<unsigned int spacedim>

5216 {

5218 private:

5223  const double
5224  V_m_f;

5226 public:

5245  OmegaFluidIncompressibility01( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
5246  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
5247  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,

5249  const double V_m_f,
5250  const unsigned int method,
5251  const double alpha = 0.0)
5252  :
5253  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 10, 9, 1, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaDualFluidIncompressibility01"),

5261  bool

5264  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
5265  double& omega,
5266  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
5267  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,

5269  const bool compute_dq)
5270  const

5273  // start indices for respective quantities
5274  const unsigned int i_grad_v_dot = 0;
5275  const unsigned int i_c_f_dot = 9;
5276  const unsigned int i_grad_u_dot = 10;
5277  const unsigned int i_eta_f = 19;
5278  const unsigned int i_F = 20;
5279 
5280  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_v_dot;
5281  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5282  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
5283  grad_v_dot[r][R] = values[i_grad_v_dot + 3 * r + R];
5284 
5285  const double c_f_dot = values[i_c_f_dot];
5286 
5287  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_u_dot;
5288  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5289  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
5290  grad_u_dot[r][R] = values[i_grad_u_dot + 3 * r + R];
5291 
5292  const double eta_f = values[i_eta_f];
5293 
5294  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F;
5295  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5296  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
5297  F[m][n] = values[i_F + m * 3 + n];
5298  const double J = determinant(F);
5299  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv;
5300  F_inv = invert(F);
5301 
5302  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_v_dot_u_dot = grad_v_dot - grad_u_dot;
5303 
5304  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
5305  {
5306  omega = -J/V_m_f * trace(F_inv * (grad_v_dot_u_dot)) * eta_f - eta_f * c_f_dot;
5307  }
5308

5310  {

5312  d_omega[i_eta_f] = -c_f_dot - J/V_m_f * trace(F_inv * (grad_v_dot_u_dot));
5313  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5314  {
5315  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
5316  {
5317  d_omega[i_grad_v_dot + 3 * r + R] = -J / V_m_f * F_inv[R][r] * eta_f;
5318  d_omega[i_grad_u_dot + 3 * r + R] = J / V_m_f * F_inv[R][r] * eta_f;
5319  }
5320  }
5321  }
5322 
5323  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
5324  {
5325 
5326  d2_omega[i_c_f_dot][i_eta_f] = d2_omega[i_eta_f][i_c_f_dot] = -1.0;
5327

5329  {

5331  {
5332  d2_omega(i_eta_f, i_grad_v_dot + 3 * r + R) = d2_omega(i_grad_v_dot + 3 * r + R, i_eta_f) = -J / V_m_f * F_inv[R][r];
5333  d2_omega(i_eta_f, i_grad_u_dot + 3 * r + R) = d2_omega(i_grad_u_dot + 3 * r + R, i_eta_f) = J / V_m_f * F_inv[R][r];
5334  }
5335  }
5336 
5337 
5338  if(compute_dq)
5339  {
5340  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5341  {
5342  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
5343  {
5344  for(unsigned int s = 0; s < 3; ++s)
5345  {
5346  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
5347  {
5348  d2_omega(i_grad_v_dot + 3 * r + R, i_F + 3 * s + S) = -J/V_m_f * (F_inv[S][s] * F_inv[R][r] - F_inv[S][r] * F_inv[R][s] ) * eta_f;
5349  d2_omega(i_grad_u_dot + 3 * r + R, i_F + 3 * s + S) = J/V_m_f * (F_inv[S][s] * F_inv[R][r] - F_inv[S][r] * F_inv[R][s] ) * eta_f;
5350  }
5351  }
5352  d2_omega(i_eta_f, i_F + 3 * r + R) = - J/V_m_f * (trace(F_inv * (grad_v_dot_u_dot)) * F_inv[R][r] - (F_inv * (grad_v_dot_u_dot * F_inv))[R][r] );
5353  }

5455  const
5456  {
5457 
5458  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F, F_inv;
5459 
5460  const double eta_f = values[6];
5461 
5462  dealii::Tensor<1,3> v_dot, u_dot, v_dot_u_dot;
5463  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5464  {
5465  v_dot[r] = values[r];
5466  u_dot[r] = values[3 + r];
5467  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
5468  F[r][S] = values[7 + 3 * r + S];
5469  }
5470  F_inv = invert(F);
5471  const double J = determinant(F);
5472  v_dot_u_dot = v_dot - u_dot;
5473 
5474  dealii::Tensor<1, 3> n__, n_;
5475  n__[0] = n[0];
5476  n__[1] = spacedim < 2 ? 0.0 : n[1];
5477  n__[2] = spacedim < 3 ? 0.0 : n[2];
5478  n_ = flip_normal ? -J * transpose(F_inv) * n__ : J * transpose(F_inv) * n__;
5479 
5480  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
5481  {
5482  sigma = eta_f * v_dot_u_dot * n_ / V_m_f;
5483  }
5484 
5485  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
5486  {
5487  d_sigma[6] = v_dot_u_dot * n_ / V_m_f;
5488  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5489  {
5490  d_sigma[r] = eta_f * n_[r] / V_m_f;
5491  d_sigma[r + 3] = -eta_f * n_[r] / V_m_f;
5492  }
5493  }
5494 
5495  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
5496  {
5497 
5498  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5499  {
5500  d2_sigma(6, r) = d2_sigma(r, 6) = n_[r] / V_m_f;
5501  d2_sigma(6, r + 3) = d2_sigma(r + 3, 6) = -n_[r] / V_m_f;
5502  }
5503 
5504  if(compute_dq)
5505  {
5506  dealii::Tensor<3,3> dn_dF;
5507  dealii::Tensor<2,3> v_dot_u_dot_dn_dF;
5508  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5509  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5510  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
5511  dn_dF[m][r][R] = F_inv[R][r] * n_[m] - F_inv[R][m] * n_[r];
5512  v_dot_u_dot_dn_dF = v_dot_u_dot * dn_dF;
5513  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5514  {
5515  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
5516  {
5517  d2_sigma(6, 7 + r * 3 + R) = v_dot_u_dot_dn_dF[r][R] / V_m_f;
5518  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
5519  {
5520  d2_sigma(k, 7 + r * 3 + R) = eta_f * dn_dF[k][r][R] / V_m_f;
5521  d2_sigma(k + 3, 7 + r * 3 + R) = -eta_f * dn_dF[k][r][R] / V_m_f;
5522  }
5523  }
5524  }
5525  }
5526  }
5527 
5528  return false;
5529  }
5530 };

5621  const bool compute_dq)
5622  const

5625  // start indices for respective quantities

5627  const unsigned int i_grad_u_dot = 9;
5628  const unsigned int i_eta_f = 18;
5629  const unsigned int i_F = 19;

5632  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5633  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
5634  grad_v_dot[r][R] = values[i_grad_v_dot + 3 * r + R];
5635

5637  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5638  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
5639  grad_u_dot[r][R] = values[i_grad_u_dot + 3 * r + R];
5640 
5641  const double eta_f = values[i_eta_f];
5642

5644  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5645  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
5646  F[m][n] = values[i_F + m * 3 + n];
5647  const double J = determinant(F);
5648  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv;
5649  F_inv = invert(F);
5650

5666  d_omega[i_grad_u_dot + 3 * r + R] = J / V_m_f * F_inv[R][r] * eta_f;
5667  }
5668  }
5669  }

5676  {

5678  d2_omega(i_eta_f, i_grad_u_dot + 3 * r + R) = d2_omega(i_grad_u_dot + 3 * r + R, i_eta_f) = J / V_m_f * F_inv[R][r];
5679  }
5680  }
5681

5684  {

5686  {
5687  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
5688  {
5689  for(unsigned int s = 0; s < 3; ++s)
5690  {
5691  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
5692  {
5693  d2_omega(i_grad_v_dot + 3 * r + R, i_F + 3 * s + S) = -J/V_m_f * (F_inv[S][s] * F_inv[R][r] - F_inv[S][r] * F_inv[R][s] ) * eta_f;
5694  d2_omega(i_grad_u_dot + 3 * r + R, i_F + 3 * s + S) = J/V_m_f * (F_inv[S][s] * F_inv[R][r] - F_inv[S][r] * F_inv[R][s] ) * eta_f;
5695  }
5696  }
5697  d2_omega(i_eta_f, i_F + 3 * r + R) = - J/V_m_f * (trace(F_inv * (grad_v_dot_u_dot)) * F_inv[R][r] - (F_inv * (grad_v_dot_u_dot * F_inv))[R][r] );
5698  }
5699  }
5700  }
5701 
5702  }
5703  return false;
5704 
5705  }
