6052 template<unsigned int spacedim>
6053 class OmegaFluidNormalCondition00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
6054 {
6055 
6056 public:
6057 
6073  OmegaFluidNormalCondition00(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_omega,
6074  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
6075  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
6076  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
6077  const unsigned int method,
6078  const double alpha = 0.0)
6079  :
6080  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 10, 0, 1, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaFluidNormalCondition00")
6081  {
6082  }
6083 
6087  bool
6088  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
6089  const double /*t*/,
6090  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
6091  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& n,
6092  double& sigma,
6093  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
6094  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
6095  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
6096  const bool compute_dq)
6097  const
6098  {
6099 
6100 
6101  // start indices for respective quantities
6102  const unsigned int i_grad_v_dot = 0;
6103  const unsigned int i_xi_dot = 9;
6104  const unsigned int i_eta = 10;
6105  const unsigned int i_F = 11;
6106 
6107  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_v_dot_ref, grad_v_dot, d;
6108  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6109  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6110  grad_v_dot_ref[r][R] = values[i_grad_v_dot + 3 * r + R];
6111 
6112  const double xi_dot = values[i_xi_dot];
6113 
6114  const double eta = values[i_eta];
6115 
6116  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F;
6117  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
6118  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
6119  F[m][n] = values[i_F + m * 3 + n];
6120  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv;
6121  F_inv = invert(F);
6122 
6123  grad_v_dot = grad_v_dot_ref * F_inv;
6124 
6125  dealii::Tensor<1, 3> n__, n_tilde, F_inv_n_tilde;
6126  n__[0] = n[0];
6127  n__[1] = spacedim < 2 ? 0.0 : n[1];
6128  n__[2] = spacedim < 3 ? 0.0 : n[2];
6129  n_tilde = transpose(F_inv) * n__;
6130 
6131  F_inv_n_tilde = F_inv * n_tilde;
6132 
6133  d = 2.0 * symmetrize(grad_v_dot);
6134 
6135  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
6136  d[m][m] += xi_dot;
6137 
6138  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
6139  {
6140  sigma = eta * (n_tilde * d) * n_tilde;
6141  }
6142 
6143  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
6144  {
6145  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
6146  for(unsigned int J = 0; J < 3; ++J)
6147  d_sigma[i_grad_v_dot + 3 * i + J] = 2.0 * eta * n_tilde[i] * F_inv_n_tilde[J];
6148  d_sigma[i_xi_dot] = eta * (n_tilde * n_tilde);
6149  d_sigma[i_eta] = (n_tilde * d) * n_tilde;
6150  }
6151 
6152  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
6153  {
6154 
6155  d2_sigma(i_xi_dot, i_eta) = d2_sigma(i_eta, i_xi_dot) = n_tilde * n_tilde;
6156  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
6157  for(unsigned int J = 0; J < 3; ++J)
6158  d2_sigma(i_eta, i_grad_v_dot + 3 * i + J) = d2_sigma(i_grad_v_dot + 3 * i + J, i_eta) = 2.0 * n_tilde[i] * F_inv_n_tilde[J];
6159 
6160  if(compute_dq)
6161  {
6162  dealii::Tensor<3,3> dn_tilde_dF, F_inv_dn_tilde_dF;
6163  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
6164  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
6165  for(unsigned int J = 0; J < 3; ++J)
6166  dn_tilde_dF[k][i][J] = -n_tilde[i] * F_inv[J][k];
6167  F_inv_dn_tilde_dF = F_inv * dn_tilde_dF;
6168  dealii::Tensor<2,3> n_tilde_dn_tilde_dF = n_tilde * dn_tilde_dF;
6169 
6170  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
6171  for(unsigned int J = 0; J < 3; ++J)
6172  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6173  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6174  d2_sigma(i_grad_v_dot + 3 * i + J, i_F + 3 * r + R) = 2.0 * eta * ( dn_tilde_dF[i][r][R] * F_inv_n_tilde[J] + F_inv_dn_tilde_dF[J][r][R] * n_tilde[i] - n_tilde[i] * F_inv[J][r] * F_inv_n_tilde[R] );
6175  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6176  {
6177  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6178  {
6179  d2_sigma(i_xi_dot, i_F + 3 * r + R) = 2.0 * eta * n_tilde_dn_tilde_dF[r][R];
6180  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
6181  for(unsigned int l = 0; l < 3; ++l)
6182  d2_sigma(i_eta, i_F + 3 * r + R) += 2.0 * ( dn_tilde_dF[l][r][R] * d[k][l] * n_tilde[k] - n_tilde[k] * grad_v_dot[k][r] * F_inv[R][l] * n_tilde[l]);
6183  }
6184  }
6185  }
6186  }
6187 
6188  return false;
6189  }
6190 };

6220 template<unsigned int spacedim>
6221 class OmegaFluidNormalCondition01 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
6222 {
6223 
6224 public:
6225 
6241  OmegaFluidNormalCondition01(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_sigma,
6242  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
6243  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
6244  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
6245  const unsigned int method,
6246  const double alpha = 0.0)
6247  :
6248  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_sigma, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 9, 0, 3, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaFluidNormalCondition01")
6249  {
6250  }
6251 
6255  bool
6256  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
6257  const double /*t*/,
6258  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
6259  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& n,
6260  double& sigma,
6261  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
6262  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
6263  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
6264  const bool compute_dq)
6265  const
6266  {
6267 
6268 
6269  // start indices for respective quantities
6270  const unsigned int i_grad_v_dot = 0;
6271  const unsigned int i_f = 9;
6272  const unsigned int i_F = 12;
6273 
6274  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_v_dot_ref, grad_v_dot, d;
6275  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6276  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6277  grad_v_dot_ref[r][R] = values[i_grad_v_dot + 3 * r + R];
6278 
6279  dealii::Tensor<1,3> f;
6280  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6281  f[r] = values[i_f + r];
6282 
6283  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F;
6284  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
6285  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
6286  F[m][n] = values[i_F + m * 3 + n];
6287  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv, C_inv;
6288  F_inv = invert(F);
6289  C_inv = F_inv * transpose(F_inv);
6290  const double J = determinant(F);
6291 
6292  grad_v_dot = grad_v_dot_ref * F_inv;
6293 
6294  dealii::Tensor<1,3> N, n_, n_tilde;
6295  N[0] = n[0];
6296  N[1] = spacedim < 2 ? 0.0 : n[1];
6297  N[2] = spacedim < 3 ? 0.0 : n[2];
6298 
6299  const double h = sqrt(N * C_inv * N);
6300  n_tilde = J * N * F_inv;
6301  n_ = n_tilde / h;
6302 
6303  dealii::Tensor<1,3> F_inv_n = F_inv * n_;
6304  const double n_tilde_f = n_tilde * f;
6305 
6306  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
6307  {
6308  sigma = - 2.0 * (n_ * grad_v_dot * n_) * (n_tilde * f);
6309  }
6310 
6311  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
6312  {
6313  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
6314  for(unsigned int N = 0; N < 3; ++N)
6315  d_sigma[i_grad_v_dot + 3 * m + N] = -2.0 * n_[m] * F_inv_n[N] * n_tilde_f;
6316  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
6317  d_sigma[i_f + i] = -2.0 * (n_ * grad_v_dot * n_) * n_tilde[i];
6318  }
6319 
6320  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
6321  {
6322 
6323  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
6324  for(unsigned int N = 0; N < 3; ++N)
6325  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
6326  d2_sigma(i_grad_v_dot + 3 * m + N, i_f + i) = d2_sigma(i_f + i, i_grad_v_dot + 3 * m + N) = -2.0 * n_[m] * F_inv_n[N] * n_tilde[i];
6327 
6328  if(compute_dq)
6329  {
6330  dealii::Tensor<2,3> dh_dF;
6331  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6332  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6333  dh_dF[r][R] = -1.0 / J * n_[r] * (N * C_inv)[R];
6334  dealii::Tensor<3,3> dn_dF, F_inv_dn_dF;
6335  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
6336  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6337  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6338  dn_dF[k][r][R] = F_inv[R][r] * n_[k] - F_inv[R][k] * n_[r] - n_[k] / h * dh_dF[r][R];
6339  F_inv_dn_dF = F_inv * dn_dF;
6340  dealii::Tensor<1,3> F_inv_f = F_inv * f;
6341 
6342 // dealii::Tensor<2,3> n_tilde_dn_tilde_dF = n_tilde * dn_tilde_dF;
6343 
6344  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
6345  for(unsigned int N = 0; N < 3; ++N)
6346  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6347  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6348  d2_sigma(i_grad_v_dot + 3 * m + N, i_F + 3 * r + R) = -2.0 * dn_dF[m][r][R] * F_inv_n[N] * n_tilde_f
6349  - 2.0 * n_[m] * F_inv_dn_dF[N][r][R] * n_tilde_f
6350  - 2.0 * n_[m] * F_inv_n[N] *(F_inv[R][r] * n_tilde_f - F_inv_f[R] * n_tilde[r])
6351  + 2.0 * n_[m] * ( F_inv[N][r] * F_inv_n[R] * n_tilde_f);
6352  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
6353  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6354  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6355  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
6356  for(unsigned int l = 0; l < 3; ++l)
6357  d2_sigma(i_f + i, i_F + 3 * r + R) += -2.0 * dn_dF[k][r][R] * grad_v_dot[k][l] * n_[l] * n_tilde[i]
6358  -2.0 * n_[k] * grad_v_dot[k][l] * dn_dF[l][r][R] * n_tilde[i]
6359  -2.0 * n_[k] * grad_v_dot[k][l] * n_[l] * ( F_inv[R][r] * n_tilde[i] - F_inv[R][i] * n_tilde[r])
6360  +2.0 * n_[k] * grad_v_dot[k][r] * F_inv[R][l] * n_[l] * n_tilde[i];
6361  }
6362  }
6363 
6364  return false;
6365  }
6366 };

6409 template<unsigned int spacedim>
6410 class OmegaLagrangeViscousDissipation00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
6411 {
6412 
6413 public:
6414 
6430  OmegaLagrangeViscousDissipation00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
6431  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
6432  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
6433  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
6434  const unsigned int method,
6435  const double alpha = 0.0)
6436  :
6437  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 9, 0, 9, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaLagrangeViscousDissipation00")
6438  {
6439  }
6440 
6444  bool
6445  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
6446  const double /*t*/,
6447  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
6448  double& omega,
6449  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
6450  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
6451  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
6452  const bool compute_dq)
6453  const
6454  {
6455 
6456  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_ref_v, grad_ref_f, F, F_inv, C_inv, grad_v, grad_f, grad_v_sym, grad_f_sym, delta;
6457  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6458  {
6459  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
6460  {
6461  grad_ref_v[r][S] = values[3 * r + S];
6462  grad_ref_f[r][S] = values[9 + 3 * r + S];
6463  F[r][S] = values[18 + 3 * r + S];
6464  }
6465  }
6466  F_inv = invert(F);
6467  C_inv = F_inv * transpose(F_inv);
6468  grad_v = grad_ref_v * F_inv;
6469  grad_v_sym = symmetrize(grad_v);
6470  grad_f = grad_ref_f * F_inv;
6471  grad_f_sym = symmetrize(grad_f);
6472  delta[0][0] = delta[1][1] = delta[2][2] = 1.0;
6473  const double J = determinant(F);
6474 
6475  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
6476  {
6477  omega = 2.0 * J * trace( grad_f * symmetrize(grad_v) );
6478  }
6479 
6480  dealii::Tensor<2,3> T_f, T_v;
6481  if(get<1>(requested_quantities) || get<2>(requested_quantities))
6482  {
6483  T_f = 2.0 * J * grad_f_sym * transpose(F_inv);
6484  T_v = 2.0 * J * grad_v_sym * transpose(F_inv);
6485  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
6486  {
6487  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6488  {
6489  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
6490  d_omega[r * 3 + S] = T_f[r][S];
6491  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
6492  d_omega[9 + r * 3 + S] = T_v[r][S];
6493  }
6494  }
6495  }
6496 
6497  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
6498  {
6499  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6500  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
6501  for(unsigned int p = 0; p < 3; ++p)
6502  for(unsigned int Q = 0; Q < 3; ++Q)
6503  d2_omega(r * 3 + S, 9 + p * 3 + Q) = d2_omega(9 + p * 3 + Q, r * 3 + S) = J * (delta[r][p] * C_inv[S][Q] + F_inv[Q][r] * F_inv[S][p]);
6504  if(compute_dq)
6505  {
6506  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv_grad_v, F_inv_grad_v_T, F_inv_grad_f, F_inv_grad_f_T;
6507  F_inv_grad_v = F_inv * grad_v;
6508  F_inv_grad_v_T = F_inv * transpose(grad_v);
6509  F_inv_grad_f = F_inv * grad_f;
6510  F_inv_grad_f_T = F_inv * transpose(grad_f);
6511 
6512  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
6513  {
6514  for(unsigned int I = 0; I < 3; ++I)
6515  {
6516  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6517  {
6518  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6519  {
6520  d2_omega(i * 3 + I, r * 3 + R + 18) = F_inv[R][r] * T_f[i][I] - J * ( F_inv_grad_f[I][r] * F_inv[R][i] + C_inv[R][I] * grad_f[i][r] + ( F_inv_grad_f[R][i] + F_inv_grad_f_T[R][i] ) * F_inv[I][r] );
6521  d2_omega(9 + i * 3 + I, r * 3 + R + 18) = F_inv[R][r] * T_v[i][I] - J * ( F_inv_grad_v[I][r] * F_inv[R][i] + C_inv[R][I] * grad_v[i][r] + ( F_inv_grad_v[R][i] + F_inv_grad_v_T[R][i] ) * F_inv[I][r] );
6522  }
6523  }
6524  }
6525  }
6526  }
6527  }
6528 
6529  return false;
6530  }
6531 };

6566 template<unsigned int spacedim>

6596  OmegaZeroTangentialFlux00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_omega,

6601  const unsigned int method,

6606  {
6607  }
6608 
6612  bool
6613  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
6614  const double /*t*/,
6615  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
6616  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& n,
6617  double& sigma,
6618  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
6619  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
6620  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
6621  const bool compute_dq)
6622  const
6623  {
6624 
6625  dealii::Tensor<1,3> u_dot, v_dot, u_dot_v_dot, t;
6626  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F, F_inv;
6627 
6628 
6629  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6630  {
6631  u_dot[r] = values[r];
6632  v_dot[r] = values[3 + r];
6633  t[r] = values[6 + r];
6634  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
6635  F[r][S] = values[9 + 3 * r + S];
6636  }
6637  F_inv = invert(F);
6638  u_dot_v_dot = u_dot - v_dot;
6639  const double J = determinant(F);
6640 
6641  dealii::Tensor<1, 3> n__, n_;
6642  n__[0] = n[0];
6643  n__[1] = spacedim < 2 ? 0.0 : n[1];
6644  n__[2] = spacedim < 3 ? 0.0 : n[2];
6645  n_ = flip_normal ? -J * transpose(F_inv) * n__ : J * transpose(F_inv) * n__;
6646 
6647  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
6648  {
6649  sigma = t * cross_product_3d(u_dot_v_dot, n_) + 0.5 * (t * n_) * (t * n_);
6650  }
6651 
6652  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
6653  {
6654  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6655  {
6656  d_sigma[r] = cross_product_3d(n_, t)[r];
6657  d_sigma[3 + r] = -cross_product_3d(n_, t)[r];
6658  d_sigma[6 + r] = cross_product_3d(u_dot_v_dot, n_)[r] + (t * n_) * n_[r];
6659  }
6660  }
6661 
6662  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
6663  {
6664  d2_sigma(6 + 0, 0) = d2_sigma(0, 6 + 0) = 0.0;
6665  d2_sigma(6 + 1, 0) = d2_sigma(0, 6 + 1) = -n_[2];
6666  d2_sigma(6 + 2, 0) = d2_sigma(0, 6 + 2) = n_[1];
6667  d2_sigma(6 + 0, 1) = d2_sigma(1, 6 + 0) = n_[2];
6668  d2_sigma(6 + 1, 1) = d2_sigma(1, 6 + 1) = 0.0;
6669  d2_sigma(6 + 2, 1) = d2_sigma(1, 6 + 2) = -n_[0];
6670  d2_sigma(6 + 0, 2) = d2_sigma(2, 6 + 0) = -n_[1];
6671  d2_sigma(6 + 1, 2) = d2_sigma(2, 6 + 1) = n_[0];
6672  d2_sigma(6 + 2, 2) = d2_sigma(2, 6 + 2) = 0.0;
6673 
6674  d2_sigma(6 + 0, 3) = d2_sigma(3, 6 + 0) = 0.0;
6675  d2_sigma(6 + 1, 3) = d2_sigma(3, 6 + 1) = n_[2];
6676  d2_sigma(6 + 2, 3) = d2_sigma(3, 6 + 2) = -n_[1];
6677  d2_sigma(6 + 0, 4) = d2_sigma(4, 6 + 0) = -n_[2];
6678  d2_sigma(6 + 1, 4) = d2_sigma(4, 6 + 1) = 0.0;
6679  d2_sigma(6 + 2, 4) = d2_sigma(4, 6 + 2) = n_[0];
6680  d2_sigma(6 + 0, 5) = d2_sigma(5, 6 + 0) = n_[1];
6681  d2_sigma(6 + 1, 5) = d2_sigma(5, 6 + 1) = -n_[0];
6682  d2_sigma(6 + 2, 5) = d2_sigma(5, 6 + 2) = 0.0;
6683 
6684  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
6685  for(unsigned int l = 0; l < 3; ++l)
6686  d2_sigma(6 + m, 6 + l) = n_[m] * n_[l];
6687 
6688  if(compute_dq)
6689  {
6690  dealii::Tensor<3,3> dn_dF;
6691  dealii::Tensor<2,3> t_dn_dF;
6692  const double t_n = t * n_;
6693  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
6694  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6695  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6696  dn_dF[m][r][R] = F_inv[R][r] * n_[m] - F_inv[R][m] * n_[r];
6697  t_dn_dF = t * dn_dF;
6698  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6699  {
6700  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6701  {
6702  d2_sigma(0, 9 + 3 * r + R) = dn_dF[1][r][R] * t[2] - dn_dF[2][r][R] * t[1];
6703  d2_sigma(1, 9 + 3 * r + R) = dn_dF[2][r][R] * t[0] - dn_dF[0][r][R] * t[2];
6704  d2_sigma(2, 9 + 3 * r + R) = dn_dF[0][r][R] * t[1] - dn_dF[1][r][R] * t[0];
6705  d2_sigma(3, 9 + 3 * r + R) = -dn_dF[1][r][R] * t[2] + dn_dF[2][r][R] * t[1];
6706  d2_sigma(4, 9 + 3 * r + R) = -dn_dF[2][r][R] * t[0] + dn_dF[0][r][R] * t[2];
6707  d2_sigma(5, 9 + 3 * r + R) = -dn_dF[0][r][R] * t[1] + dn_dF[1][r][R] * t[0];
6708  d2_sigma(6, 9 + 3 * r + R) = -dn_dF[1][r][R] * u_dot_v_dot[2] + dn_dF[2][r][R] * u_dot_v_dot[1] + t_dn_dF[r][R] * n_[0] + t_n * dn_dF[0][r][R];
6709  d2_sigma(7, 9 + 3 * r + R) = -dn_dF[2][r][R] * u_dot_v_dot[0] + dn_dF[0][r][R] * u_dot_v_dot[2] + t_dn_dF[r][R] * n_[1] + t_n * dn_dF[1][r][R];
6710  d2_sigma(8, 9 + 3 * r + R) = -dn_dF[0][r][R] * u_dot_v_dot[1] + dn_dF[1][r][R] * u_dot_v_dot[0] + t_dn_dF[r][R] * n_[2] + t_n * dn_dF[2][r][R];
6711  }
6712  }
6713  }
6714  }
6715 
6716  return false;
6717  }

6813  {
6814  u_dot[r] = values[r];
6815  v_dot[r] = values[3 + r];
6816 
6817  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
6818  F[r][S] = values[7 + 3 * r + S];
6819  }
6820  const double t = values[6];
6821 
6822  F_inv = invert(F);
6823  u_dot_v_dot = u_dot - v_dot;
6824  const double J = determinant(F);
6825 
6826  dealii::Tensor<1, 3> n__, n_;
6827  n__[0] = n[0];
6828  n__[1] = spacedim < 2 ? 0.0 : n[1];
6829  n__[2] = spacedim < 3 ? 0.0 : n[2];
6830  n_ = flip_normal ? -J * transpose(F_inv) * n__ : J * transpose(F_inv) * n__;
6831 
6832  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
6833  {
6834  sigma = t * u_dot_v_dot * n_;
6835  }
6836 
6837  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
6838  {
6839  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6840  {
6841  d_sigma[r] = t * n_[r];
6842  d_sigma[3 + r] = -t * n_[r];
6843  }
6844  d_sigma[6] = u_dot_v_dot * n_;
6845  }
6846 
6847  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
6848  {
6849 
6850  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6851  {
6852  d2_sigma(r,6) = d2_sigma(6,r) = n_[r];
6853  d2_sigma(3 + r,6) = d2_sigma(6,r + 3) = -n_[r];
6854  }
6855 
6856  if(compute_dq)
6857  {
6858  dealii::Tensor<3,3> dn_dF;
6859  dealii::Tensor<2,3> u_dot_v_dot_dn_dF;
6860  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
6861  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6862  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6863  dn_dF[m][r][R] = F_inv[R][r] * n_[m] - F_inv[R][m] * n_[r];
6864  u_dot_v_dot_dn_dF = u_dot_v_dot * dn_dF;
6865  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6866  {
6867  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6868  {
6869  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
6870  {
6871  d2_sigma(k, 7 + r * 3 + R) = t * dn_dF[k][r][R];
6872  d2_sigma(3 + k, 7 + r * 3 + R) = -t * dn_dF[k][r][R];
6873  }
6874  d2_sigma(6, 7 + r * 3 + R) = u_dot_v_dot_dn_dF[r][R];
6875  }
6876  }
6877  }
6878  }
6879 
6880  return false;
6881  }
6882 };
6883 
6884 
6885 
6899 template<unsigned int spacedim>
6900 class OmegaZeroTangentialFlux2D00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
6901 {
6902 
6903 public:
6904 
6920  OmegaZeroTangentialFlux2D00(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_omega,
6921  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
6922  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
6923  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
6924  const unsigned int method,
6925  const double alpha = 0.0)
6926  :
6927  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 2, 2, 1, 4, method, alpha, "OmegaZeroTangentialFlux2D00")
6928  {
6929  }
6930 
6934  bool
6935  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
6936  const double /*t*/,
6937  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
6938  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& n,
6939  double& sigma,
6940  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
6941  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
6942  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
6943  const bool compute_dq)
6944  const
6945  {
6946  (void)compute_dq;
6947  Assert(!compute_dq, dealii::ExcMessage("The alpha-family for temporal discretization is not currently implemented!"));
6948  Assert(spacedim == 2, dealii::ExcMessage("This is currently only implemented in two dimensions!"));
6949 
6950  const double dv_0 = values[0] - values[2];
6951  const double dv_1 = values[1] - values[3];
6952  const double lambda = values[4];
6953 
6954  dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim> n_, t_;
6955  dealii::Tensor<2, spacedim> F;
6956  F[0][0] = values[5];
6957  F[0][1] = values[6];
6958  F[1][0] = values[7];
6959  F[1][1] = values[8];
6960  n_ = transpose(invert(F)) * n;
6961  n_ *= 1.0 / sqrt(n_ * n_);
6962  t_[0] = n_[1];
6963  t_[1] = -n_[0];
6964 
6965  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
6966  {
6967  sigma = lambda * ( t_[0] * dv_0 + t_[1] * dv_1 );
6968  }
6969 
6970  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
6971  {
6972  d_sigma[0] = lambda * t_[0];
6973  d_sigma[1] = lambda * t_[1];
6974  d_sigma[2] = -lambda * t_[0];
6975  d_sigma[3] = -lambda * t_[1];
6976  d_sigma[4] = t_[0] * dv_0 + t_[1] * dv_1;
6977  }
6978 
6979  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
6980  {
6981  d2_sigma(0,4) = d2_sigma(4,0) = t_[0];
6982  d2_sigma(1,4) = d2_sigma(4,1) = t_[1];
6983  d2_sigma(2,4) = d2_sigma(4,2) = -t_[0];
6984  d2_sigma(3,4) = d2_sigma(4,3) = -t_[1];
6985  }
6986 
6987  return false;
6988  }
6989 };

7006 template<unsigned int spacedim>
7007 class OmegaElectricalLoading : public incrementalFE::Omega<0, spacedim>
7008 {
7009 
7010 public:
7011 
7015  double
7016  j_bar = 0.0;
7017 
7021  double
7022  phi = 0.0;
7023 
7027  double
7028  R_el = 0.0;
7029 
7035  unsigned int
7036  loading_type = 0;
7037 
7049  OmegaElectricalLoading( const std::vector<const dealii::GalerkinTools::IndependentField<0, spacedim>*> C,
7050  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
7051  const unsigned int method,
7052  const double alpha)
7053  :
7054  Omega<0, spacedim>(C, global_data, 1, 0, 1, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaElectricalLoading")
7055  {
7056  }
7057 
7058  bool get_values_and_derivatives(const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
7059  const double /*t*/,
7060  double& omega,
7061  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
7062  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
7063  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
7064  const bool /*compute_d2q*/)
7065  const
7066  {
7067  const double j_ap = values[0];
7068  const double phi_ap = values[1];
7069 
7070  if(loading_type == 0)
7071  {
7072  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
7073  omega = -j_bar * phi_ap;
7074 
7075  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
7076  {
7077  d_omega[0] = 0.0;
7078  d_omega[1] = -j_bar;
7079  }
7080 
7081  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
7082  {
7083  d2_omega(0,0) = 0.0;
7084  d2_omega(1,1) = 0.0;
7085  d2_omega(0,1) = d2_omega(1,0) = 0.0;
7086  }
7087  }
7088  else if(loading_type == 1)
7089  {
7090  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
7091  omega = -j_ap * (phi_ap - phi);
7092 
7093  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
7094  {
7095  d_omega[0] = -(phi_ap - phi);
7096  d_omega[1] = -j_ap;
7097  }
7098 
7099  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
7100  {
7101  d2_omega(0,0) = 0.0;
7102  d2_omega(1,1) = 0.0;
7103  d2_omega(0,1) = d2_omega(1,0) = -1.0;
7104  }
7105  }
7106  else if(loading_type == 2)
7107  {
7108  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
7109  omega = -0.5 / R_el * phi_ap * phi_ap;
7110 
7111  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
7112  {
7113  d_omega[0] = 0.0;
7114  d_omega[1] = -1.0 / R_el * phi_ap;
7115  }
7116 
7117  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
7118  {
7119  d2_omega(0,0) = 0.0;
7120  d2_omega(1,1) = -1.0 / R_el;
7121  d2_omega(0,1) = d2_omega(1,0) = 0.0;
7122  }
7123  }
7124  else
7125  {
7126  Assert(false, dealii::ExcMessage("Unknown loading type!"));
7127  }
7128 
7129  return false;
7130  }
7131 };

7149 template<unsigned int spacedim>
7150 class OmegaFluidDissipation00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
7151 {
7152 
7153 private:
7154 
7158  const double
7159  D;
7160 
7164  const double
7165  V_m_f;
7166 
7167 
7168 public:
7169 
7189  OmegaFluidDissipation00(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
7190  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
7191  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
7192  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
7193  const double D,
7194  const double V_m_f,
7195  const unsigned int method,
7196  const double alpha = 0.0)
7197  :
7198  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 0, 3, 0, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaFluidDissipation00"),
7199  D(D),
7200  V_m_f(V_m_f)
7201  {
7202  }
7203 
7207  bool
7208  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
7209  const double /*t*/,
7210  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
7211  double& omega,
7212  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
7213  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
7214  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
7215  const bool compute_dq)
7216  const
7217  {
7218 
7219  const double Idot11 = values[0];
7220  const double Idot21 = values[1];
7221  const double Idot31 = values[2];
7222  const double F11 = values[3];
7223  const double F21 = values[4];
7224  const double F31 = values[5];
7225  const double F41 = values[6];
7226  const double F51 = values[7];
7227  const double F61 = values[8];
7228  const double F71 = values[9];
7229  const double F81 = values[10];
7230  const double F91 = values[11];
7231 
7232  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
7233  {
7234  omega = (1.0/2.0)*V_m_f*(Idot11*(Idot11*(((F11)*(F11)) + ((F41)*(F41)) + ((F71)*(F71))) + Idot21*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot31*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91)) + Idot21*(Idot11*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot21*(((F21)*(F21)) + ((F51)*(F51)) + ((F81)*(F81))) + Idot31*(F21*F31 + F51*F61 + F81*F91)) + Idot31*(Idot11*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91) + Idot21*(F21*F31 + F51*F61 + F81*F91) + Idot31*(((F31)*(F31)) + ((F61)*(F61)) + ((F91)*(F91)))))/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7235  }
7236 
7237  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
7238  {
7239  d_omega(0) = V_m_f*(Idot11*(((F11)*(F11)) + ((F41)*(F41)) + ((F71)*(F71))) + Idot21*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot31*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91))/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7240  d_omega(1) = V_m_f*(Idot11*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot21*(((F21)*(F21)) + ((F51)*(F51)) + ((F81)*(F81))) + Idot31*(F21*F31 + F51*F61 + F81*F91))/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7241  d_omega(2) = V_m_f*(Idot11*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91) + Idot21*(F21*F31 + F51*F61 + F81*F91) + Idot31*(((F31)*(F31)) + ((F61)*(F61)) + ((F91)*(F91))))/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7242  }
7243 
7244  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
7245  {
7246  d2_omega(0,0) = V_m_f*(((F11)*(F11)) + ((F41)*(F41)) + ((F71)*(F71)))/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7247  d2_omega(0,1) = V_m_f*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81)/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7248  d2_omega(0,2) = V_m_f*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91)/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7249  d2_omega(1,0) = V_m_f*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81)/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7250  d2_omega(1,1) = V_m_f*(((F21)*(F21)) + ((F51)*(F51)) + ((F81)*(F81)))/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7251  d2_omega(1,2) = V_m_f*(F21*F31 + F51*F61 + F81*F91)/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7252  d2_omega(2,0) = V_m_f*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91)/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7253  d2_omega(2,1) = V_m_f*(F21*F31 + F51*F61 + F81*F91)/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7254  d2_omega(2,2) = V_m_f*(((F31)*(F31)) + ((F61)*(F61)) + ((F91)*(F91)))/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7255  if(compute_dq)
7256  {
7257  d2_omega(0,3) = V_m_f*(-(F51*F91 - F61*F81)*(Idot11*(((F11)*(F11)) + ((F41)*(F41)) + ((F71)*(F71))) + Idot21*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot31*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91)) + (2*F11*Idot11 + F21*Idot21 + F31*Idot31)*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71))/(D*((F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)));
7258  d2_omega(0,4) = V_m_f*(F11*Idot21*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71) + (F41*F91 - F61*F71)*(Idot11*(((F11)*(F11)) + ((F41)*(F41)) + ((F71)*(F71))) + Idot21*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot31*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91)))/(D*((F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)));
7259  d2_omega(0,5) = V_m_f*(F11*Idot31*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71) - (F41*F81 - F51*F71)*(Idot11*(((F11)*(F11)) + ((F41)*(F41)) + ((F71)*(F71))) + Idot21*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot31*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91)))/(D*((F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)));
7260  d2_omega(0,6) = V_m_f*((F21*F91 - F31*F81)*(Idot11*(((F11)*(F11)) + ((F41)*(F41)) + ((F71)*(F71))) + Idot21*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot31*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91)) + (2*F41*Idot11 + F51*Idot21 + F61*Idot31)*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71))/(D*((F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)));
7261  d2_omega(0,7) = V_m_f*(F41*Idot21*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71) - (F11*F91 - F31*F71)*(Idot11*(((F11)*(F11)) + ((F41)*(F41)) + ((F71)*(F71))) + Idot21*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot31*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91)))/(D*((F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)));
7262  d2_omega(0,8) = V_m_f*(F41*Idot31*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71) + (F11*F81 - F21*F71)*(Idot11*(((F11)*(F11)) + ((F41)*(F41)) + ((F71)*(F71))) + Idot21*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot31*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91)))/(D*((F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)));
